of%20munitions%20and%20supplies%20for%20Moscow's%20war%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKim%20is%20likely%20to%20head%20by%20armored%20train%20later%20this%20month%20to%20Vladivostok%2C%20on%20Russia's%20Pacific%20coast%20not%20far%20from%20North%20Korea%2C%20to%20meet%20with%20Putin%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20said%20Putin%20wanted%20artillery%20shells%20and%20antitank%20missiles%20from%20North%20Korea%2C%20and%20Kim%20could%20even%20travel%20to%20Moscow%2C%20but%20that%20was%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKim%20is%20reported%20to%20be%20seeking%20advanced%20technology%20for%20satellites%20and%20nuclear-powered%20submarines%20as%20well%20as%20food%20aid%20for%20his%20impoverished%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20at%20Seoul's%20unification%20ministry%2C%20which%20handles%20inter-Korean%20relations%2C%20said%20various%20developments%20%26quot%3Bindicated%26quot%3B%20the%20growing%20possibility%20of%20an%20arms%20deal%20between%20Pyongyang%20and%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20form%20of%20cooperation%20between%20North%20Korea%20and%20neighboring%20countries%20must%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20way%20that%20does%20not%20undermine%20international%20norms%20and%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20said%20last%20week%20that%20despite%20its%20denials%2C%20North%20Korea%20supplied%20infantry%20rockets%20and%20missiles%20to%20Russia%20in%202022%20for%20use%20by%20the%20privately%20controlled%20Wagner%20military%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Minister%20Sergei%20Shoigu%20traveled%20to%20North%20Korea%20in%20July%20seeking%20to%20acquire%20additional%20munitions%20for%20the%20war%2C%20Watson%20said%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Diplomatic%20isolation%20-%3Cbr%3E%5CnPark%20Won-gon%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Ewhat%20University%20in%20Seoul%2C%20said%20both%20Pyongyang%20and%20Moscow%20needed%20to%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20away%20from%20diplomatic%20isolation%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20a%20summit%20would%20send%20a%20message%20to%20Washington%2C%20which%20is%20ramping%20up%20defence%20cooperation%20with%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20South%20Korea%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Japan%20have%20recently%20been%20strengthening%20cooperation%2C%20including%20the%20Camp%20David%20summit%2C%20North%20Korea%20and%20Russia%20also%20need%20to%20showcase%20their%20cooperation%20in%20a%20symbolic%20diplomatic%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Britain%2C%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20said%20that%20any%20deal%20to%20increase%20cooperation%20between%20Russia%20and%20North%20Korea%20would%20violate%20Security%20Council%20resolutions%20forbidding%20arms%20deals%20with%20Pyongyang%20--%20resolutions%20Moscow%20itself%20had%20endorsed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20following%20Shoigu's%20visit%20to%20Pyongyang%2C%20another%20group%20of%20Russian%20officials%20traveled%20to%20North%20Korea%20for%20follow-up%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECho%20Han-bum%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Korea%20Institute%20for%20National%20Unification%2C%20said%20that%20sanctions%20will%20do%20little%20to%20stop%20Russia%20and%20North%20Korea%20from%20trading%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20strategic%20competition%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20have%20virtually%20neutralised%20the%20current%20UN%20Security%20Council%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Cho%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20and%20Pyongyang%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20worries%26quot%3B%20about%20sanctions%20as%20both%20countries%20were%20already%20operating%20under%20an%20array%20of%20Western%20punitive%20measures%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20military%20cooperation%20between%20the%20two%20was%20likely%20%26quot%3Bunstoppable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20last%20month%20sanctioned%20three%20entities%20accused%20of%20seeking%20to%20facilitate%20arms%20deals%20between%20North%20Korea%20and%20Russia%20as%20Washington%20tightened%20restrictions%20on%20support%20for%20Moscow's%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Treasury%20Department%20said%20that%20Russia%20was%20continuing%20to%20use%20up%20munitions%20and%20lose%20heavy%20equipment%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20turn%20to%20its%20small%20pool%20of%20allies%2C%20including%20North%20Korea%2C%20for%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20have%20claimed%20some%20progress%20in%20their%20ongoing%20counteroffensive%2C%20but%20Putin%20on%20Monday%20again%20said%20the%20attempt%20to%20retake%20land%20lost%20since%20Russia's%20February%202022%20invasion%20had%20been%20unsuccessful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20that%20it%20is%20stalling.%20It%20is%20a%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20Turkish%20leader%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20in%20the%20Black%20Sea%20resort%20city%20of%20Sochi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%20today%20this%20is%20what%20it%20looks%20like.%20Let's%20see%20what%20happens%20next.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20the%20likely%20meeting%20between%20Kim%20and%20Putin%20came%20as%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20said%20he%20had%20visited%20his%20war-torn%20country's%20frontline%20eastern%20Donetsk%20region%2C%20posting%20a%20video%20of%20himself%20meeting%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693887000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fogvps718_kim-jong-un-reuters_625x300_28_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fkim-jong-un-to-meet-puti