the%20newly%20built%20international%20convention%20and%20exhibition%20centre%2C%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan.%C2%A0Since%20the%20G20%20is%20a%20high-profile%20meeting%2C%20several%20restrictions%20are%20imposed%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district%20including%20the%20suspension%20of%20all%20online%20delivery%20and%20commercial%20services%20during%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20cloud%20kitchens%2C%20commercial%20establishments%2C%20markets%2C%20food%20delivery%2C%20and%20commercial%20delivery%20services%20will%20be%20shut%20for%20three%20days%20in%20the%20New%C2%A0Delhi%C2%A0district%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can't%20allow%20cloud%20kitchen%20and%20food%20delivery%20services.%20Internet%20delivery%20companies%20such%20as%20Amazon%20and%20Flipkart%20will%20also%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20operate%20in%20the%20controlled%20zone.%20Delivery%20executives%20can%20take%20medicines%20and%20essential%20items%2C%E2%80%9D%20Special%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Traffic)%20SS%20Yadav%20said%20on%20September%204%20during%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-sourcepos%3D%5C%227%3A1-7%3A213%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCloud%20kitchens%20and%20food%20deliveries%2C%20or%20any%20commercial%20deliveries%20like%20Amazon%20deliveries%2C%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20as%20we%20have%20stopped%20commercial%20services%20in%20the%20NDMC%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Special%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20SS%20Yadav%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-sourcepos%3D%5C%227%3A1-7%3A213%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20the%20delivery%20of%20essential%20medical%20items%2C%20including%20lab%20reports%20and%20sample%20collections%2C%20will%20be%20permitted%20throughout%20the%20city.%C2%A0Vehicles%20for%20hotels%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20other%20significant%20installations%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20District%20that%20are%20involved%20in%20housekeeping%2C%20catering%2C%20trash%20disposal%2C%20etc.%20will%20be%20permitted%20following%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Essential%20services%20such%20as%20postal%20and%20medical%20services%2C%20sample%20collections%20by%20path%20labs%20will%20be%20allowed%20throughout%20Delhi%2C''%20Mr%20Yadav%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20officer%20also%20added%20that%20barring%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20station%2C%20metro%20services%20will%20not%20be%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''There%20might%20be%20closure%20of%20gates%20for%2010-15%20minutes%20at%20stations%20due%20to%20VIP%20movement%20and%20security%20restrictions.%20But%20apart%20from%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan%20(Supreme%20Court)%2C%20metro%20services%20will%20not%20be%20affected%20at%20other%20stations%2C''%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20all%20Central%20government%20offices%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20will%20be%20closed%20from%20September%208%20to%2010%20considering%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693885980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fg79usnc_swiggy-generic_625x300_17_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-swiggy-zomato-amazon-deliveries-not-allowed-from-september-8-10-in-new-delhi-district-4360149%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22All%20cloud%20kitchens%2C%20commercial%20establishments%2C%20markets%2C%20food%20delivery%2C%20and%20commercial%20delivery%20services%20will%20be%20shut%20for%20three%20days%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-swiggy-zomato-amazon-deliveries-not-allowed-from-september-8-10-in-new-delhi-district-4360149%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-swiggy-zomato-amazon-deliveries-not-allowed-from-september-8-10-in-new-delhi-district-4360149%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-summit-swiggy-zomato-amazon-deliveries-not-allowed-from-september-8-10-in-new-delhi-district-4360149%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Whether%20Polls%20Are%20Sooner%20or%20Later%2C%20INDIA%20Must%20Face%20Fundamental%20Questions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20taken%20nine%20years%20for%20the%20disparate%20Opposition%20parties%20to%20realise%20that%20if%20they%20do%20not%20hang%20together%20they%20will%20hang%20separately%20to%20fight%20the%20monolithic%20and%20powerful%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20And%20the%20INDIA%20block%20they%20have%20formed%20offers%20perhaps%20the%20best%20opportunity%20to%20take%20on%20the%20mighty%20ruling%20party%2C%20they%20all%20seem%20to%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20out%20of%20their%20first%20major%20conclave%20in%20Mumbai%20emerged%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20images%20seen%20in%20India%20for%20some%20time.%20Long-term%20rivals%20in%20the%20same%20room%20%E2%80%94%20CPI(M)%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%94%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa634b669-ec6c-40a4-9756-be3210287911%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fa634b669-ec6c-40a4-9756-be3210287911%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693971091038000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2EcraKa4EVXnMKSuVS6avR%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etying%20a%20rakhi%20to%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20regional%20parties%20putting%20aside%20their%20innate%20hostility%20to%20the%20Congress.%20These%20are%20optics%2C%20for%20sure%2C%20but%20perceptions%20do%20matter%20and%20certainly%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20party%20colleagues%20take%20this%20grouping%20seriously%20enough%20to%20continuously%20mock%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnited%20Opposition%20fronts%20have%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20past.%20The%20Janata%20Party%2C%20formed%20within%20weeks%20of%20the%20Emergency%20being%20lifted%20in%201977%2C%20had%20trounced%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20It%20contained%20members%20of%20the%20old%20Congress%2C%20the%20socialists%20and%20the%20Jan%20Sangh.%20The%20National%20Front%20of%201989%2C%20which%20was%20spearheaded%20by%20V.P.%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%2C%20formed%20two%20governments%20in%20two%20years.%20The%20United%20Front%20of%2013%20parties%20which%20was%20formed%20after%20the%201996%20elections%20also%20formed%20two%20governments.%20Every%20one%20of%20these%20experiments%20failed%20due%20to%20internal%20contradictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20saying%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20also%20not%20dissolve.%20Nor%20can%20anyone%20guarantee%20that%20even%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20internal%20dissensions%20will%20not%20crop%20up%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20fighting%20state%20elections%20or%20seat%20sharing%20for%202024.%20Already%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20been%20making%20strong%20statements%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%20the%20latter%20is%20not%20amused%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'Ready%20to%20Face%20Raids'%3A%20INDIA%20Parties%20Resolve%20to%20Fight%20Polls%20Together%2C%20Announce%204%20Committees%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-election-lok-sabha-together-four-committees%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ready%20to%20Face%20Raids%E2%80%99%3A%20INDIA%20Parties%20Resolve%20to%20Fight%20Polls%20Together%2C%20Announce%204%20Committees%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeat%20sharing%20and%20putting%20up%20joint%20candidates%20will%20pose%20an%20even%20bigger%20challenge.%20Will%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20agree%20to%20work%20for%20a%20CPI(M)%20candidate%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%20Will%20Congress%20workers%20support%20an%20NCP%20candidate%20in%20Maharashtra%3F%20How%20will%20parties%20convince%20their%20cadre%20to%20campaign%20for%20rivals%3F%20The%20Congress%20has%20always%20regarded%20Sharad%20Pawar%20with%20suspicion.%20His%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20departure%20to%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government%20has%20only%20added%20to%20it.%20When%20the%20two%20met%20recently%2C%20the%20Congress%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F285baf74-5a45-4ad8-a754-929bf65ab0b7%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F285baf74-5a45-4ad8-a754-929bf65ab0b7%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693971091038000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0V9NSXpnWrnBH-htiCRraX%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemanded%20answers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bihar%20is%20going%20to%20be%20another%20challenge.%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20his%20father%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20are%20well%20disposed%20towards%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20is%20Nitish%20Kumar%3F%20And%20where%20does%20Kumar%20stand%2C%20anyway%3F%20He%20was%20very%20much%20present%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%2C%20but%20he%20has%20ambitions%20of%20his%20own.%20He%20will%20not%20be%20amused%20if%20he%20sees%20another%20leader%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20not%20arbitrary%2C%20abstract%20questions.%20They%20will%20have%20to%20be%20tackled%20very%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most-asked%20question%20today%20is%2C%20whether%20INDIA%20will%20be%20able%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20No%20one%20can%20give%20a%20firm%20answer.%20The%20BJP%20is%20not%20going%20to%20sit%20idle%20and%20will%20have%20plans%20of%20its%20own.%20While%20the%20conclave%20was%20going%20on%2C%20the%20government%20called%20a%20special%20five%20day%20session%20of%20parliament%20and%20speculation%20is%20on%20about%20what%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20announce%20in%20it.%20Simultaneously%2C%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20discuss%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%20%E2%80%95%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20states%20and%20the%20Centre.%20The%20BJP%20has%20set%20the%20political%20agenda%20and%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20busy%20attacking%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20elections%20get%20closer%2C%20will%20the%20BJP%20pull%20a%20stunt%20to%20galvanise%20its%20supporters%20and%20consolidate%20its%20vote%3F%20Already%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20asked%20about%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20in%202019%20in%20which%2040%20Indian%20soldiers%20died%20and%20which%20led%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98surgical%20strike%E2%80%99%20which%20then%20enthused%20voters%2C%20appealing%20to%20nationalist%20sentiments.%20What%20will%20be%20the%20enthusing%20move%20this%20time%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP's%20Propaganda%2C%20Probe%20Agencies%20and%20Partisan%20Media%3A%20The%20Challenges%20Before%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20Bloc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-propaganda-probe-agencies-and-partisan-media-the-challenges-for-opposition-india-bloc%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Propaganda%2C%20Probe%20Agencies%20and%20Partisan%20Media%3A%20The%20Challenges%20Before%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20INDIA%20Bloc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20just%20been%20set%20up.%20What%20if%20elections%20are%20called%20in%20the%20Parliament%20session%20%E2%80%94%20does%20it%20have%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20fight%20as%20a%20joint%20front%3F%20The%20BJP%20may%20be%20counting%20on%20surprise.%20Two%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F45d8bdfe-b42e-4b8c-be9e-32bc5f57ef90%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F45d8bdfe-b42e-4b8c-be9e-32bc5f57ef90%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1693971091038000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0cchO73mPFF7HpOv_SjhXL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evoter%20surveys%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20suggested%20that%20if%20the%20elections%20were%20to%20be%20held%20now%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20will%20win.%20Of%20course%2C%20surveys%20often%20go%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20the%20BJP%20was%20supposed%20to%20win%20in%20Karnataka%20recently%20and%20earlier%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20which%20was%20highlighted%20by%20television%20channels.%20Yet%2C%20the%20fundamental%20question%20of%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20preparedness%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bonhomie%20between%20various%20parties%20was%20heartwarming%2C%20but%20clearly%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20its%20work%20cut%20out%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20whenever%20they%20are%20held.%20Indeed%2C%20an%20earlier%20election%20will%20probably%20work%20in%20its%20favour%20because%20there%20will%20not%20be%20any%20time%20for%20differences%20to%20crop%20up.%20It%20may%20not%20win%20%E2%80%94%20and%20chances%20are%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20front%20can%20give%20the%20BJP%20a%20tough%20fight.%20This%20time%20round%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20not%20find%20the%20going%20so%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%