led%20%E2%80%98India%3A%20UN%20experts%20alarmed%20by%20continuing%20abuses%20in%20Manipur'%2C%20the%20Permanent%20Mission%20of%20India%20expressed%20disappointment%20and%20surprise%20that%20the%20SPMHs%20chose%20to%20issue%20the%20press%20release%20without%20waiting%20for%20the%2060%20days%20period%20for%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20joint%20communication%20issued%20on%20the%20same%20topic%20on%20August%2029%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20mission%20expressed%20hope%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20SPMH%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20objective%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20assessment%2C%20based%20on%20the%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20hoped%20that%20the%20SPMH%20would%20%E2%80%9Crefrain%20from%20commenting%20on%20the%20developments%2C%20which%20have%20no%20relevance%20to%20the%20mandate%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20Council%20and%20abide%20by%20the%20established%20procedure%20for%20issuing%20news%20releases%20and%20wait%20for%20inputs%20sought%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20before%20doing%20so.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Indian%20mission%20reiterated%20that%20India%20is%20a%20democratic%20country%2C%20with%20an%20abiding%20commitment%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20to%20promoting%20and%20protecting%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20our%20people.%20%26quot%3BIndian%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20and%20security%20forces%20are%20committed%20to%20dealing%20with%20law-and-order%20situations%20strictly%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20legal%20certainty%2C%20necessity%2C%20proportionality%20and%20non-discrimination%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20news%20release%2C%20the%20UN%20experts%20had%20said%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cappalled%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20reports%20and%20images%20of%20gender-based%20violence%20targeting%20hundreds%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20and%20predominantly%20of%20the%20Kuki%20ethnic%20minority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20alleged%2