slide%20victory%20this%20week%20to%20become%20the%20ninth%20president-elect%20of%20the%20city-state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWidely%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20Singapore%20and%20Asia's%20most%20influential%20and%20respected%20political%20leaders%20and%20economists%2C%20his%20election%20to%20the%20highest%20office%20marks%20a%20watershed%20moment%20in%20Singaporean%20politics.%20He%20secured%20an%20overwhelming%2070.4%20percent%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20a%20three-way%20race%20that%20involved%20two%20credible%20Singaporean%20Chinese%20contenders%20from%20the%20majority%20community.%20Tharman%20launched%20his%20presidential%20campaign%20with%20the%20slogan%20%26quot%3BRespect%20for%20All.%26quot%3B%20Chinese%2C%20Malays%2C%20and%20Indians%20constitute%2074%25%2C%2013%25%2C%20and%209%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20political%20career%2C%20Tharman%20has%20been%20known%20for%20championing%20racial%20harmony%2C%20social%20cohesion%2C%20and%20meritocracy%2C%20a%20message%20that%20resonated%20with%20Singaporeans.%20After%20winning%20the%20election%2C%20he%20noted%20how%20%26quot%3Brace%20was%20not%20the%20only%20factor%20in%20the%20contest%20and%20believed%20that%20the%20results%20showed%20that%20Singaporeans%20want%20a%20non-partisan%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKV%20Rao%2C%20one%20of%20the%20city-state's%20respected%20industry%20and%20community%20leaders%2C%20explained%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20mandate%2C%20above%20all%2C%20is%20an%20emphatic%20vote%20for%20merit.%20His%20win%20is%20a%20great%20way%20forward%20for%20Singapore%20and%20the%20world.%20Singaporeans%20have%20demonstrated%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20they%20stand%20for%20unity%20and%20not%20divisiveness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20on%20February%2025%2C%201957%2C%20in%20Singapore%2C%20Tharman%20is%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Chinese%20mother%20and%20a%20Tamil%20father%2C%20former%20Emeritus%20Professor%20K%20Shanmugaratnam%2C%20a%20medical%20scientist%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bfather%20of%20pathology%20in%20Singapore%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20founded%20the%20Singapore%20Cancer%20Registry.%20Educated%20at%20the%20LSE%2C%20Cambridge%2C%20and%20Harvard%20Kennedy%20School%2C%20he%20is%20married%20to%20Jane%20Yumiko%20Ittogi%2C%20a%20Singaporean%20lawyer%20of%20mixed%20Chinese%20Japanese%20ancestry.%20First%20elected%20MP%20in%202001%20with%20the%20ruling%20People's%20Action%20Party%2C%20he%20has%20been%20elected%20four%20times%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharman%20is%20one%20of%20Singapore's%20most%20seasoned%20politicians%20widely%20respected%20for%20an%20exemplary%20life%20in%20public%20service%2C%20improving%20social%20and%20economic%20policies%20for%20all%20citizens.%20He%20has%20been%20Senior%20Minister%20and%20Coordinating%20Minister%20for%20Social%20Policies%2C%20advising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20Economic%20policies%2C%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Minister%20for%20Finance%2C%20and%20Minister%20of%20Education.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Monetary%20Authority%20(MAS)%20of%20Singapore%20and%20Singapore's%20GIC%20Board%2C%20one%20of%20the%20three%20investment%20entities%20that%20manage%20the%20country's%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternationally%2C%20he%20has%20made%20his%20mark%2C%20too.%20He%20chairs%20the%20Group%20of%20Thirty%2C%20a%20global%20council%20of%20economic%20and%20financial%20leaders%20from%20the%20public%20and%20private%20sectors%20and%20academia%20and%20led%20the%20G20%20Eminent%20Persons%20Group%20on%20Global%20Financial%20Governance%2C%20which%20in%20October%202018%20proposed%20reforms%20in%20development%20finance%20and%20the%20international%20monetary%20system%20to%20advance%20a%20new%2C%20cooperative%20international%20order.%20He%20earlier%20chaired%20the%20International%20Monetary%20and%20Financial%20Committee%20(IMFC)%20for%20four%20years%3B%20he%20was%20its%20first%20Asian%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProf%20Kishore%20Mahbubani%2C%20one%20of%20Singapore's%20leading%20diplomats%20and%20a%20global%20public%20intellectual%2C%20recently%20wrote%20on%20his%20LinkedIn%20Post%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20would%20help%20to%20have%20a%20President%20who%20is%20globally%20respected.%20Few%20Singaporeans%20are%20as%20highly%20respected%20in%20key%20capitals%2C%20especially%20Washington%20D.C.%20and%20Beijing%2C%20as%20Tharman%20is%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%3A%20%26quot%3BQuite%20amazingly%2C%20for%20a%20deep%20and%20serious%20thinker%2C%20he%20also%20has%20a%20remarkable%20sense%20of%20humour.%20He%20always%20has%20a%20twinkle%20in%20his%20eye%20and%20a%20ready%20smile%20on%20his%20face.%20His%20big%20thoughts%20and%20good%20cheer%20will%20also%20help%20to%20lift%20our%20spirits%2C%20in%20good%20times%20and%20bad%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Tharman's%20win%2C%20many%20in%20India%20are%20hopeful%20for%20what%20lies%20ahead%20for%20Singapore-India%20ties.%20The%20close%20relations%20and%20high%20regard%20in%20which%20he%20is%20held%20by%20Indian%20political%20and%20business%20leadership%2C%20including%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20bode%20well%20for%20the%20future.%20Congratulating%20him%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20closely%20with%20you%20to%20further%20strengthen%20the%20India-Singapore%20Strategic%20Partnership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20public%20service%20and%20leadership%2C%20Mr%20Tharman%20Shanmugaratnam%20has%2C%20Indian%20industry%20looking%20to%20his%20presidency%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20foster%20an%20even%20closer%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20Together%2C%20we%20can%20provide%20an%20inclusive%20model%20for%20development%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Kris%20Gopalakrishnan%2C%20a%20Padma%20Bhushan%20awardee%20and%20the%20former%20CEO%20and%20Managing%20director%20of%20Infosys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Singapore%2C%20Tharman%20has%20worked%20throughout%20his%20career%20to%20uplift%20educational%20performance%20and%20social%20resilience%20in%20the%20Indian%20Singaporean%20community%20through%20chairing%20the%20Board%20of%20Trustees%20of%20the%20Singapore%20Indian%20Development%20Association%20(SINDA).%20Singapore's%20President-elect%20instinctively%20understands%20India's%20ethos%20and%20civilisational%20heritage.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20a%20great%20love%20and%20respect%20for%20Indian%20culture%2C%20history%2C%20and%20the%20arts%20and%20actively%20supports%20their%20pursuit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20President%20of%20the%20Singapore%20Indian%20Fine%20Arts%20Society%20(SIFAS)%2C%20where%20Tharman%20is%20on%20the%20Board%20of%20Advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20inaugural%20Arun%20Jaitley%20Memorial%20Lecture%2C%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20July%202022%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20listening%20to%20an%20outstanding%20musical%20performance%20called%20Triveni%2C%20named%20after%20Triveni%20Sangam%2C%20the%20mythical%20confluence%20of%20rivers%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%2C%20and%20Saraswati%2C%20by%20three%20of%20India's%20most%20accomplished%20classical%20musicians%20-%20Zakir%20Hussain%2C%20Kala%20Ramnath%2C%20and%20Jayanthi%20Kumaresh%20playing%20the%20Tabla%2C%20Violin%20and%20Veena%2C%20traditions%20of%20North%20and%20South%2C%20I%20realized%20it%20was%20not%20about%20their%20individual%20genius%2C%20it%20was%20about%20each%20of%20them%20listening%20to%20the%20other%2C%20teasing%2C%20co-creating%2C%20and%20co-empowering.%20It%20was%20a%20collective%20genius.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplying%20this%20idea%20to%20India%20as%20a%20nation%2C%20he%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20no%20lack%20of%20individual%20top%20talents.%20But%20what%20it%20has%20to%20develop%20is%20that%20collective%20capability%2C%20co-empowerment%2C%20co-creation%2C%20and%20having%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20trust%20amongst%20each%20other.%20Co-empowerment%20and%20co-creation%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20between%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20states%2C%20and%20the%20panchayats%20at%20the%20district%20and%20village%20level%2C%20and%20across%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20faiths%2C%20white%20and%20blue%20collar%2C%20and%20gender.%20Develop%20this%20collective%20capability%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years.%20That%20is%20India's%20promise.%20And%20if%20India%20succeeds%2C%20as%20I%20believe%20it%20will%2C%20it%20will%20not%20just%20uplift%20one-fifth%20of%20the%20world's%20population%2C%20it%20will%20also%20be%20showing%20the%20way%20for%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20assumes%20office%2C%20Singapore's%20new%20President-elect%20will%20be%20closely%20watched%20in%20India.%20Tharman's%20presidency%20presents%20an%20invaluable%20opportunity%20to%20further%20strengthen%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20His%20stature%2C%20experience%2C%20maturity%2C%20and%20connection%20with%20India%20are%20expected%20to%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20cementing%20the%20ties%20to%20promote%20greater%20cooperation%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20Singapore%2C%20India%2C%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EPreeti%20Dawra%20is%20a%20columnist%2C%20strategist%2C%20and%20a%20leading%20member%20of%20the%20Singapore-Indian%20diaspora)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693879560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F9gk9t0f_tharman-shanmugaratnam-reuters_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fsingapores-new-indian-origin-president-will-be-closely-watched-in-india-4359413%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singapore%2C%20a%20multi-ethnic%20and%20diverse%20nation%2C%20witnessed%20a%20historic%20presidential%20ele