od%20just%20five%20miles%20south%20of%20Beverly%20Hills%2C%20where%20I%20had%20spent%20the%20previous%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalaga%20told%20me%20the%20cheapest%20home%20on%20the%20market%20right%20now%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20costs%2052%20million%20pesos%2C%20or%20around%20%24915%2C000.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20two%20properties%20that%20were%20listed%20for%20sale%20at%20the%20time%20of%20my%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalaga%20told%20me%20homes%20in%20Beverly%20Hills%20are%20rarely%20sold%20to%20outsiders%2C%20as%20many%20who%20live%20there%20are%20regarded%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BOld%20Money%26quot%3B%20of%20Cebu.%20And%20when%20they%20do%20go%20on%20sale%2C%20the%20price%20is%20often%20in%20the%20millions%2C%20Balaga%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20homes%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20are%20typically%20listed%20for%20at%20least%20100%20million%20pesos%2C%20or%20%241.75%20million.%20For%20comparison%2C%20the%20median%20price%20of%20homes%20in%20Cebu%20City%20is%20listed%20at%20%24141%2C270%2C%20per%20data%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasia.uli.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2FULI-Home-Attainability-Index-report_-28-May-Finalised.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUrban%20Land%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20owners%20initially%20wanted%20to%20sell%20their%20homes%2C%20but%20changed%20their%20mind%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20Balaga%20said%20about%20Beverly%20Hills%2C%20adding%20that%20residents%20usually%20only%20sell%20to%20people%20they%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20families%20have%20lived%20in%20their%20Beverly%20Hills%20homes%20for%20generations.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22cebu%20philippines%20beverly%20hills%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64eed63c96b7920019ca2dfe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20gated%20mansion%20in%20Cebu%2C%20Philippines.%