20president%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20according%20to%20a%20US%20official.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fkim-jong-un-looks-set-to-meet-vladimir-putin-as-russia-tries-to-buy-north-korean-weapons-to-bolster-ukraine-campaign-12955227%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fkim-jong-un-looks-set-to-meet-vladimir-putin-as-russia-tries-to-buy-north-korean-weapons-to-bolster-ukraine-campaign-12955227%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fkim-jong-un-looks-set-to-meet-vladimir-putin-as-russia-tries-to-buy-north-korean-weapons-to-bolster-ukraine-campaign-12955227%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aditya%20L1%20successfully%20undergoes%20the%20second%20earth-bound%20manoeuvre%3A%20Isro%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693865544000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103369949%2Cimgsize-323060.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faditya-l1-successfully-undergoes-the-second-earth-bound-manoeuvre-isro%2Farticleshow%2F103369951.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aditya%20L1%2C%20the%20first%20space%20based%20Indian%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%20underwent%20the%20second%20earth-bound%20manoeuvre%20successfully%2C%20during%20the%20early%20hours%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Isro%20said.%20Isro's%20Telemetry%2C%20Tracking%20and%20Command%20Network%20(ISTRAC)%20carried%20out%20the%20operation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PTI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Faditya-l1-successfully-undergoes-the-second-earth-bound-manoeuvre-isro%2Farticleshow%2F103369951.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO's%20Aditya%20L1%20Successfully%20Undergoes%202nd%20Earth-Bound%20Manoeuvre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAditya%20L1%2C%20the%20first%20space%20based%20Indian%20mission%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%20underwent%20the%20second%20earth-bound%20manoeuvre%20successfully%2C%20during%20the%20early%20hours%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20ISRO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO's%20Telemetry%2C%20Tracking%20and%20Command%20Network%20(ISTRAC)%20carried%20out%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%20Earth-bound%20manoeuvre%20(EBN%232)%20is%20performed%20successfully%20from%20ISTRAC%2C%20Bengaluru.%20ISTRAC%2FISRO's%20ground%20stations%20at%20Mauritius%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Port%20Blair%20tracked%20the%20satellite%20during%20this%20operation.%20The%20new%20orbit%20attained%20is%20282%20km%20x%2040225%20km%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20manoeuvre%20(EBN%233)%20is%20scheduled%20for%20September%2010%2C%202023%2C%20around%2002%3A30%20Hrs.%20IST%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20space%20based%20observatory%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%20from%20a%20halo%20orbit%20around%20first%20sun-earth%20Lagrangian%20point%20(L1)%2C%20which%20is%20located%20roughly%201.5%20million%20km%20from%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20earth-bound%20manoeuvre%20was%20successfully%20performed%20on%20September%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spacecraft%20will%20undergo%20two%20more%20earth-bound%20orbital%20manoeuvres%20before%20placing%20in%20the%20transfer%20orbit%20towards%20the%20Lagrange%20point%20L1.%20Aditya-L1%20is%20expected%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20intended%20orbit%20at%20the%20L1%20point%20after%20about%20127%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO's%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV-C57)%20on%20September%202%20had%20successfully%20launched%20the%20Aditya-L1%20spacecraft%2C%20from%20the%20Second%20Launch%20Pad%20of%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Centre%20(SDSC)%2C%20Sriharikota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20flight%20duration%20of%2063%20minutes%20and%2020%20seconds%2C%20Aditya-L1%20spacecraft%20was%20successfully%20injected%20into%20an%20elliptical%20orbit%20of%20235x19500%20km%20around%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ISRO%2C%20a%20satellite%20placed%20in%20the%20halo%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%20point%20has%20the%20major%20advantage%20of%20continuously%20viewing%20the%20Sun%20without%20any%20occultation%20%2Feclipses.%20This%20will%20provide%20a%20greater%20advantage%20of%20observing%20the%20solar%20activities%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20space%20weather%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20carries%20seven%20scientific%20payloads%20indigenously%20developed%20by%20ISRO%20and%20national%20research%20laboratories%20including%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIA)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Inter%20University%20Centre%20for%20Astronomy%20and%20Astrophysics%20(IUCAA)%2C%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20payloads%20are%20to%20observe%20the%20photosphere%2C%20chromosphere%20and%20the%20outermost%20layers%20of%20the%20Sun%20(the%20corona)%20using%20electromagnetic%20and%20particle%20and%20magnetic%20field%20detectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20special%20vantage%20point%20L1%2C%20four%20payloads%20directly%20view%20the%20Sun%20and%20the%20remaining%20three%20payloads%20carry%20out%20in-situ%20studies%20of%20particles%20and%20fields%20at%20the%20Lagrange%20point%20L1%2C%20thus%20providing%20important%20scientific%20studies%20of%20the%20propagatory%20effect%20of%20solar%20dynamics%20in%20the%20interplanetary%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suits%20of%20Aditya%20L1%20payloads%20are%20expected%20to%20provide%20the%20most%20crucial%20information%20to%20understand%20the%20problem%20of%20coronal%20heating%2C%20coronal%20mass%20ejection%2C%20pre-flare%20and%20flare%20activities%20and%20their%20characteristics%2C%20dynamics%20of%20space%20weather%2C%20propagation%20of%20particles%20and%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20scientists%2C%20there%20are%20five%20Lagrangian%20points%20(or%20parking%20areas)%20between%20the%20Earth%20and%20the%20Sun%20where%20a%20small%20object%20tends%20to%20stay%20if%20put%20there.%20The%20Lagrange%20Points%20are%20named%20after%20Italian-French%20mathematician%20Joseph-Louis%20Lagrange%20for%20his%20prize-winning%20paper%20--%20%26quot%3BEssai%20sur%20le%20Probl%C3%A8me%20des%20Trois%20Corps%2C%201772.%26quot%3B%20These%20points%20in%20space%20can%20be%20used%20by%20spacecraft%20to%20remain%20there%20with%20reduced%20fuel%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Lagrange%20point%2C%20the%20gravitational%20pull%20of%20the%20two%20large%20bodies%20(the%20Sun%20and%20the%20Earth)%20equals%20the%20necessary%20centripetal%20force%20required%20for%20a%20small%20object%20to%20move%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693865160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fo9edtd1_aditya-l1-_625x300_03_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-aditya-l1-successfully-undergoes-2nd-earth-bound-manoeuvre-4360041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ISRO's%20Telemetry%2C%20Tracking%20and%20Command%20Network%20(ISTRAC)%20carried%20out%20the%20operation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-aditya-l1-successfully-undergoes-2nd-earth-bound-manoeuvre-4360041%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-aditya-l1-successfully-undergoes-2nd-earth-bound-manoeuvre-4360041%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-aditya-l1-successfully-undergoes-2nd-earth-bound-manoeuvre-4360041%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cop%20arrests%20son%20for%20gang-rape%20of%20Raipur%20sisters%2C%20seeks%20transfer%22%2C%22conte