dian%20model%E2%80%99%20outside%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20DMK%20office%20in%20Delhi%2C%20it%20marks%20an%20inflexion%20point%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20bid%20to%20signal%20it%20is%20not%20just%20another%20regional%20party%20content%20with%20supporting%20parties%20for%20power%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20but%20that%20it%20wishes%20to%20have%20its%20imprint%20nationally%20on%20any%20alternative%20contesting%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fmk-stalin-kick-start-2024-election-campaigning-new-podcast-181851%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20podcast%20%E2%80%9Cis%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20letters%20to%20the%20public%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EUngalil%20Oruvan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20DMK%20mouthpiece%20%3Cem%3EMurasoli%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Ungalil%20Oruvan%20is%20also%20the%20title%20of%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20autobiography%2C%20which%20has%20been%20translated%20into%20English%20%5Bfrom%20Tamil%5D%20as%20One%20Among%20You.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Speaking%20for%20India%E2%80%99%20%3Cspan%3Ehas%20been%20produced%20by%20Populous%20Empowerment%20Network%20(PEN)%2C%20that%20also%20looks%20after%20the%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20political%20affairs%20and%20outreach%20programmes.%20This%20has%20been%20founded%20by%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%20Sabareesan.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20PEN%20representative%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CConsider%20this%20the%20start%20of%20campaigning%20for%20the%202024%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20being%20upfront%20and%20political%2C%20the%20podcast%2C%20sources%20say%2C%20is%20deliberately%20intended%20as%20a%20counter%20to%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20fortnightly%20radio%20show%2C%20%E2%80%98Mann%20ki%20baat%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20centres%20on%20the%20PM%20himself.%20Also%2C%20within%20INDIA%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20help%20Stalin%20and%20the%20DMK%20carve%20out%20a%20space%20for%20themselves%20and%20use%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20of%20social%20justice%20to%20build%20recognition%20for%20what%20they%20stand%20for%20clearly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20this%20podcast%20series%20is%20that%20I%2C%20Muthuvel%20Karunanidhi%20Stalin%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20leader%20of%20DMK%2C%20the%20third-largest%20party%20in%20the%20Parliament%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20as%20someone%20who%20is%20one%20among%20you%2C%20wants%20to%20speak%20for%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Stalin%20in%20the%20inaugural%20show.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20BJP%20May%20End%20Up%20Tying%20Itself%20in%20Knots%20By%20Attacking%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20May%20End%20Up%20Tying%20Itself%20in%20Knots%20By%20Attacking%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20podcast%2C%20out%20on%20Monday%20(September%204)%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP-led%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%20since%202014.%20Stalin%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20violation%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20corrode%20the%20identity%20and%20rights%20of%20the%20states.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20charged%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20of%20using%20religion%20to%20hide%20its%20failures%20and%20shortcomings%2C%20as%20it%20had%20not%20succeeded%20in%20fulfilling%20poll%20promises%20or%20implementing%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fspeaking-for-india-podcast-bjp-is-using-religion-as-a-weapon-to-hide-its-shortcomings-stalin-says%2Farticle67269005.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EINDIA%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20restore%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20social%20justice%2C%20secular%20politics%2C%20socialism%2C%20equity%2C%20social%20harmony%2C%20state%20autonomy%2C%20federalism%20and%20unity%20in%20diversity%20thrive%20in%20their%20full%20glory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20this%20INDIA%20alliance%20that%20is%20going%20to%20save%20India.%20If%20we%20want%20to%20prevent%20the%20whole%20of%20India%20from%20becoming%20Manipur%20and%20Haryana%20which%2C%20unfortunately%20fell%20victim%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20communal%20politics%20and%20hate-inciting%20policies%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20must%20win%2C%E2%80%9D%20Stalin%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fspeaking-for-india-podcast-bjp-is-using-religion-as-a-weapon-to-hide-its-shortcomings-stalin-says%2Farticle67269005.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reports%20him%20saying%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20not%20been%20given%20a%20single%20special%20scheme%20in%20these%20nine%20years%20of%20BJP%20rule.%20The%20present%20BJP%20Union%20government%20was%20only%20functioning%20as%20a%20vengeful%20body%20against%20state%20governments%2C%20Stalin%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20only%20want%20to%20destroy%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20state%20governments%2C%20which%20are%20directly%20responsible%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PEN%20representative%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20future%20episodes%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20bring%20in%20guest%20speakers.%20We%20will%20also%20include%20responses%20to%20the%20public%20and%20media%20reactions%20to%20the%20previous%20episodes.%20Whether%20the%20episodes%20will%20air%20on%20a%20weekly%20or%20fortnightly%20basis%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20decided.%20This%20may%20also%20change%20depending%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20how%20close%20the%20elections%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20podcast%20is%20aimed%20at%20young%20students%20and%20first-time%20voters%2C%20with%20an%20intention%20of%20reaching%20them%20on%20digital%20platforms%20like%20Spotify%2C%20YouTube%2C%20Soundcloud%20and%20Amazon%20Music.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20hear%20the%20podcast%20on%20the%20morning%20news%20in%20Tamil%20channels%20and%20on%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20personal%20social%20media%20handles%2C%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DMK%20has%20been%20ahead%20in%20the%20communications%20game%20ever%20since%20it%20began%2C%20having%20its%20roots%20in%20the%20Dravidian%20movement%20and%20its%20close%20relationship%20to%20progressive%20and%20popular%20Tamil%20cinema.%20After%20the%20era%20of%20print%20media%20began%20to%20be%20overpowered%20by%20audio-visual%20media%2C%20the%20Sun%20group%20with%20cable%20and%20then%20a%20satellite%20TV%20network%20provided%20a%20model%20for%20other%20regional%20parties%20to%20have%20their%20own%20communication%20offer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20podcast%20is%20the%20latest%20communication%20pipeline%20being%20explored%20by%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693858481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2F06200018%2FScreenshot-2022-05-06-at-8.00.11-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2