ill-treatment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20(among%20other%20incidents)%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Evideo%20of%20two%20Kuki%20women%20being%20sexually%20assaulted%20in%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20experts%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cappalled%20by%20the%20reports%20and%20images%20of%20gender-based%20violence%20targeting%20hundreds%20of%20women%20and%20girls%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20and%20predominantly%20of%20the%20Kuki%20ethnic%20minority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20statement%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20alleged%20violence%20includes%20gang%20rape%2C%20parading%20women%20naked%20in%20the%20street%2C%20severe%20beatings%20causing%20death%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-after-80-year-old-meitei-woman-burnt-alive-in-her-own-home-family-says-police-yet-to-act%5C%22%3Eburning%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20alive%20or%20dead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20particularly%20concerning%20that%20the%20violence%20seems%20to%20have%20been%20preceded%20and%20incited%20by%20hateful%20and%20inflammatory%20speech%20that%20spread%20online%20and%20offline%20to%20justify%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20against%20the%20Kuki%20ethnic%20minority%2C%20particularly%20women%2C%20on%20account%20of%20their%20ethnicity%20and%20religious%20belief%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20welcomed%20fact-finding%20missions%20conducted%20by%20lawyers%20and%20human%20rights%20activists%20in%20Manipur%2C%20but%20noted%20reports%20that%20such%20initiatives%20were%20being%20responded%20to%20with%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20fact-finding%20mission%2C%20by%20the%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India%20(EGI)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feditorsguild.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEGI-report-on-Manipur.pdf%5C%22%3Esubmitted%20its%20findings%20three%20days%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20only%20for%20the%20Manipur%20police%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-editors-guild-fact-finding-team-cites-revoked-sec-66a%5C%22%3Efile%20an%20FIR%20against%20it%20soon%20after%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEGI%E2%80%99s%20report%20had%20criticised%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20internet%20shutdown%20and%20said%20that%20the%20media%20based%20out%20of%20Imphal%20had%20turned%20into%20%E2%80%9CMeitei%20media%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20responded%20to%20the%20report%20and%20accused%20the%20EGI%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctrying%20to%20create%20more%20clashes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20fact-finding%20team%20that%20has%20seen%20legal%20action%20after%20publishing%20a%20report%20on%20Manipur.%20In%20July%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-fir-fact-finding-team%5C%22%3Ea%20case%20was%20registered%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Annie%20Raja%2C%20Nisha%20Siddhu%20and%20Deeksha%20Dwivedi%2C%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%E2%80%99s%20team%20in%20Manipur%20and%20had%20said%20in%20their%20report%20that%20Manipur%20was%20seeing%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20experts%20also%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20violence%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20rage%20over%20four%20months%20after%20it%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20apparent%20slow%20and%20inadequate%20response%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20including%20law%20enforcement%2C%20to%20stem%20physical%20and%20sexual%20violence%20and%20hate%20speech%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20press%20release%20quoted%20the%20experts%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20observers%20have%20also%20criticised%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20not%2