usinessinsider.com%2F50-once-beloved-cars-that-have-been-discontinued-2019-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%3A%20Temple%20Murals%20Have%20Brought%20Out%20the%20Swaminarayan%20vs%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20Tensions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F05000022%2FGadhvi.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20man%20who%20defaced%20murals%20depicting%20the%20deity%20Hanuman%20in%20a%20Gujarat%20temple%20belonging%20to%20the%20Swaminarayan%20sect%20on%20Saturday%20(September%202)%20was%20released%20from%20judicial%20custody%20on%20Rs%2010%2C000%20bail%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeshgujarat.com%2F2023%2F09%2F04%2Fharshad-gadhvi-and-others-get-bail-in-salangpur-mural-attack-case%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeshGujarat%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20police%20had%20arrested%20him%20and%20two%20others%20who%20filmed%20the%20incident%20on%20Sunday%20(September%204).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDeshGujarat%2Fstatus%2F1697878333311037494%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20which%20has%20since%20gone%20viral%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Harshad%20Gadhvi%20was%20seen%20rubbing%20ink%20on%20the%20murals%20and%20attacking%20them%20with%20an%20axe%20before%20being%20overpowered%20by%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20complaint%20by%20an%20official%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fgujarat-murals-vandalised-gujarat-police-three-arrested-8922977%2F%5C%22%3Epolice%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20against%20Gadhvi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20two%20others%2C%20invoking%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20including%20295A%2C%20which%20relates%20to%20acts%20intended%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%20through%20insults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDesh