e%20include%20asking%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20to%20intervene%20and%20restrain%20leaders%20of%20the%20Swaminarayan%20sect%20from%20making%20statements%20about%20Hindu%20gods%20and%20goddesses%2C%20and%20not%20allowing%20Swaminarayan%20devotees%20to%20install%20the%20gods%20and%20goddesses%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20in%20the%20sect%E2%80%99s%20temples%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693852881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fman-who-vandalised-hanuman-murals-in-gujarat-out-on-bail%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20people%20say%20the%20murals%20insult%20the%20deity%20Hanuman%2C%20who%20is%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20devoted%20to%20Ram%20and%20Sita.%20A%20man%20recently%20granted%20bail%20was%20heard%20shouting%20%E2%80%9Chail%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%9D%20as%20he%20defaced%20the%20murals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Party's%20Assets%20Shot%20Up%20By%20152%25%20In%20A%20Year%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20assets%20declared%20by%20eight%20national%20parties%20in%202021-22%20was%20Rs%208%2C829.16%20crore%2C%20up%20from%20Rs%207%2C297.62%20crore%20during%202020-21%2C%20poll%20rights%20body%20ADR%20said%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%2C%20an%20electoral%20reform%20advocacy%20group%2C%20in%20its%20report%20analysed%20the%20assets%20and%20liabilities%20declared%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20INC%2C%20NCP%2C%20BSP%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPI(M)%2C%20AITC%2C%20and%20NPEP%20-%20the%20eight%20national%20parties%20-%20for%20FY%202020-21%20and%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20financial%20year%202020-21%2C%20the%20BJP%20declared%20assets%20worth%20Rs%204%2C990%20crore%2C%20up%20by%2021.17%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%206%2C046.81%20crore%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ADR%2C%20in%202020-21%2C%20the%20declared%20assets%20of%20Congress%20were%20Rs%20691.11%20crore%2C%20which%20shot%20up%20by%2016.58%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%20805.68%20crore%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20was%20the%20only%20national%20party%20to%20show%20a%20decrease%20in%20its%20annual%20declared%20assets%2C%20its%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20assets%20of%20BSP%20between%202020-21%20and%202021-22%20decreased%20by%205.74%20per%20cent%20-%20from%20Rs%20732.79%20crore%20to%20Rs%20690.71%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20assets%20of%20TMC%20increased%20from%20Rs%20182.001%20crore%20in%202020-21%20to%20Rs%20458.10%20crore%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20151.70%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20ADR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20liabilities%20for%20FY%202020-21%20declared%20by%20the%20national%20parties%20was%20Rs%20103.55%20crore.%20The%20Congress%20declared%20liabilities%20of%20Rs%2071.58%20crore%20-%20the%20highest%2C%20followed%20by%20CPI(M)%20with%20Rs%2016.109%20crore%2C%20ADR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20FY%202021-22%2C%20Congress%20again%20was%20at%20the%20top%20with%20liabilities%20of%20Rs%2041.95%20crore%2C%20followed%20by%20CPI%20(M)%20and%20BJP%2C%20which%20declared%20liabilities%20worth%20Rs%2012.21%20crore%20and%20Rs%205.17%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%202020-21%20and%202021-22%2C%20five%20parties%20declared%20a%20decrease%20in%20liabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINC%20declared%20a%20decrease%20in%20its%20liabilities%20by%20Rs%2029.63%20crore%2C%20BJP%20by%20Rs%206.03%20crore%2C%20CPI(M)%20by%20Rs%203.89%20crore%2C%20AITC%20by%20Rs%201.30%20crore%2C%20and%20NCP%20by%20Rs%201%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20capital%2Freserve%20fund%20set%20aside%20by%20the%20national%20parties%20during%20FY%202020-21%20was%20Rs%207%2C194%20crore%2C%20and%20Rs%208%2C766%20crore%20for%20FY%202021-22%2C%20after%20adjusting%20for%20liabilities%2C%20the%20ADR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20FY%202021-22%2C%20the%20ADR%20said%20the%20BJP%20declared%20the%20highest%20capital%20with%20Rs%206%2C041.64%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20CPI(M)%20followed%20it%20with%20RS%20763.73%20crore%20and%20Rs%20723.56%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20FY%202021-22%2C%20the%20National%20People's%20Party%20declared%20having%20a%20fund%20of%20Rs%201.82%20crore%2C%20the%20least%2C%20followed%20by%20CPI%2C%20which%20declared%20having%20Rs%2015.67%20crore%20in%20its%20coffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ADR%20said%20national%20parties%20failed%20to%20adhere%20to%20the%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20guidelines%20that%20direct%20parties%20to%20declare%20details%20of%20the%20financial%20institutions%2C%20banks%2C%20or%20agencies%20from%20whom%20loans%20were%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guidelines%20specify%20that%20the%20parties%20should%20state%20the%20%26quot%3Bterms%20of%20repayment%20of%20term%20loans%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20due%20date%20such%20as%20a%20year%2C%201-5%20years%2C%20or%20payable%20after%205%20years%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reform%20body%20also%20said%20that%20details%20of%20loans%20given%20by%20the%20parties%20in%20cash%20or%20kind%20should%20be%20specified%20and%20if%20it%20constitutes%20more%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20loans%2C%20the%20nature%20and%20amount%20of%20such%20loans%20should%20be%20declared%20specifically%20by%20them%20-%20a%20detail%20none%20of%20the%20national%20parties%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICAI%20guidelines%20on%20auditing%2C%20which%20were%20also%20endorsed%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20remain%20only%20on%20paper%20and%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20actively%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20political%20parties%20in%20disclosing%20details%20of%20their%20income%2C%20the%20ADR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%2