e.%20Listeners%20use%20the%20episodes%20as%20peaceful%20background%20music%20for%20sleep%2C%20meditation%2C%20or%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProviding%20the%20odd%20niche%20has%20proven%20lucrative.%20One%20creator%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20previous%20job%20to%20make%20white-noise%20shows%20full-time%2C%20broke%20down%20for%20Bloomberg%20reporter%20Ashley%20Carman%20last%20year%20that%20he%20was%20paid%20out%20%2412.25%20per%201%2C000%20listens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20his%20podcast's%20popularity%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-06-01%2Fhow-to-make-money-on-spotify-a-white-noise-podcast-could-bring-you-big-bucks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20added%20up%20to%20%2418%2C375%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Spotify%2C%20though%2C%20not%20all%20streams%20are%20created%20equal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20company's%20own%20estimates%2C%20Spotify%20could%20save%20%2438%20million%20annually%20steering%20listeners%20away%20from%20white%20noise%20and%20toward%20more%20lucrative%20programming%20for%20the%20company%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsletters%2F2023-08-17%2Fwhite-noise-podcasters-are-costing-spotify-38-million-a-year%3Fsref%3DExbtjcSG%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0internal%20memo%20obtained%20by%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Spotify%20spokesperson%20told%20Bloomberg%20the%20plan%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20come%20to%20fruition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-to-cut-lucrative-white-noise-podcasters-from-ad-program-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693850718000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f612ad1b7ced0019c7d3ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%