ess%20in%20every%20field%2C%20including%20administration%2C%20the%20Army%20and%20the%20corporate%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20women%20to%20make%20their%20own%20decisions%20and%20become%20financially%20self-reliant.%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20copy%20men%2C%20they%20are%20not%20better%20than%20you%2C%20keep%20yourselves%20original%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20gave%20three%20mantras%20to%20the%20female%20students%20--%20never%20get%20stressed%20as%20nothing%20is%20achieved%20by%20that%2C%20never%20be%20afraid%20of%20failure%20and%20if%20a%20good%20idea%20comes%20to%20your%20mind%2C%20implement%20it%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20youngsters%20not%20to%20get%20overly%20competitive%20and%20said%20they%20should%20choose%20their%20careers%20in%20accordance%20with%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20day%20is%20not%20far%20when%20women%20will%20get%20their%20due%20representation%20in%20Parliament%20and%20legislative%20assemblies%20through%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution.%20He%20asserted%20that%20if%20women%20get%20this%20reservation%20soon%2C%20India%20will%20become%20a%20world%20power%20before%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20education%20for%20women%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20by%20educating%20a%20boy%2C%20only%20one%20family%20achieves%20progress%2C%20but%20when%20a%20girl%20gets%20educated%2C%20several%20families%20benefit%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%20asked%20by%20a%20student%20on%20women's%20safety%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said%20it%20is%20not%20only%20the%20work%20of%20the%20government%20machinery%20but%20the%20society%2C%20individuals%20and%20institutions%20will%20have%20to%20make%20joint%20efforts%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20environment%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20anti-social%20elements%20should%20be%20dealt%20with%20strictly%2C%20he%20expressed%20happiness%20that%20the%20country%20is%20about%20to%20change%20the%20penal%20code%20made%20by%20the%20British.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president%20said%20he%20derived%20all%20his%20strength%20from%20his%20maternal%20grandmother%2C%20paternal%20grandmother%2C%20mother%20and%20wife.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20many%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20my%20five-decade-long%20public%20life%2C%20but%20these%20women%20stood%20behind%20me%20as%20firm%20as%20a%20rock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20change%20in%20the%20attitude%20towards%20women%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Dhankhar%20said%20he%20has%20promoted%20the%20gender-neutral%20word%20%26quot%3Bchairperson%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3Bchairman%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BPanel%20of%20Vice-Chairman%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BPanel%20of%20Vice-Chairperson%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20have%20appointed%2050%20per%20cent%20women%20in%20the%20panel%20of%20the%20deputy%20chairman%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20their%20performance%20has%20been%20excellent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20also%20said%20whenever%20he%20decides%20the%20names%20of%20delegation%20members%20for%20a%20trip%20within%20the%20country%20or%20abroad%2C%20he%20gives%20priority%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20have%20been%20many%20attempts%20to%20hinder%20the%20progress%20of%20women%20but%20now%2C%20society's%20attitude%20towards%20them%20is%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%202019%2C%2078%20women%20MPs%20were%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20world%20cannot%20achieve%20progress%20without%20the%20contribution%20of%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20the%20role%20of%20women%20scientists%20in%20the%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan%20and%20the%20Aditya%20Mission%2C%20he%20said%20India%20will%20change%20the%20world%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20its%20women's%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20my%20visits%20abroad%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20that%20a%20representative%20from%20India%20is%20viewed%20with%20great%20respect.%20Ten%20years%20ago%2C%20India%20was%20counted%20among%20the%20weak%20five%20countries%20and%20today%2C%20India%20is%20among%20the%20top%20five%20economies%20of%20the%20world%20and%20soon%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20third-largest%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20wastage%20of%20natural%20resources%2C%20such%20as%20electricity%2C%20water%20and%20fuel%2C%20should%20be%20stopped%2C%20Dhankhar%20said%20human%20beings%20are%20the%20trustees%20of%20these%20resources%2C%20which%20should%20be%20used%20according%20to%20their%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president%20appealed%20to%20youngsters%20to%20perform%20their%20fundamental%20duties%20alongside%20enjoying%20their%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20there%20should%20be%20no%20compromise%20on%20economic%20nationalism%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20little%20monetary%20gains%20while%20wondering%20why%20articles%20such%20as%20toys%20and%20earthen%20lamps%20for%20Diwali%20decoration%20should%20come%20from%20outside%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20his%20former%20professors%20present%20in%20the%20auditorium%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%2C%20who%20is%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Rajasthan%20University%2C%20said%20it%20was%20an%20auspicious%20day%20for%20him%20as%20he%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20his%20teachers%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20Teacher's%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudesh%20Dhankhar%2C%20Vice-Chancellor%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20University%2C%20Professor%20Rajeev%20Jain%2C%20principal%20of%20the%20Maharani%20Mahavidyalaya%2C%20Professor%20Nimali%20Singh%20and%20other%20teachers%20were%20present%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not