elfare%20and%20sports%20minister%20and%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esanatana%20dharma%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20kicked%20up%20a%20political%20storm.%20Stalin%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20has%20led%20to%20multiple%20stalwarts%20in%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20claiming%20that%20the%20Dravidian%20leader%20had%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgenocide%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Hindus.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20political%20battle%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20deeply%20rooted%20disagreement%20between%20ideologues%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20social%20justice%20politics%20on%20one%20level%2C%20and%20historical%20differences%20between%20the%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20and%2019th-century%20reformists%20on%20another.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Saturday%20(September%202)%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20conference%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatana%20Ozhippu%20Maanaadu%E2%80%99%20%5B%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conclave%E2%80%99%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20organised%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Progressive%20Writers%20and%20Artists%20Association%20to%20critique%20the%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20congratulate%20the%20organisers%20for%20calling%20the%20conference%20as%20%E2%80%98eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%98opposing%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20certain%20things%20which%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20and%20we%20cannot%20merely%20oppose.%20Mosquitoes%2C%20dengue%2C%20corona%20and%20malaria%20are%20things%20which%20we%20cannot%20oppose%2C%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20them.%20Sanatanam%20is%20also%20like%20this.%20Eradication%20and%20not%20opposing%20sanatanam%20has%20to%20be%20our%20first%20task%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20triggered%20a%20backlash%20from%20the%20BJP%20rank%20and%20file%2C%20with%20its%20IT%20cell%20head%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1697951451333763243%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3EAmit%20Malviya%20interpreting%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccall%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20genocide%E2%80%9D%20of%20sanatanis%2C%20who%20he%20claimed%20comprise%20%E2%80%9C80%25%20%5Bof%20the%5D%20population%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20took%20the%20matter%20up%20to%20challenge%20the%20newly-formed%20INDIA%20opposition%20bloc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20son%20of%20a%20chief%20minister%20%5Ba%20reference%20to%20Udhayanidhi%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20son%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%5D%20has%20called%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20%E2%80%A6%20For%20vote%20bank%20and%20appeasement%20politics%2C%20these%20people%20have%20called%20for%20the%20eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%20This%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20our%20culture%2C%20history%20and%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DMK%20leader%20quickly%20responded%20to%20say%20that%20his%20statement%20was%20being%20twisted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20called%20for%20the%20genocide%20of%20people%20who%20are%20following%20sanatana%20dharma.%20Sanatana%20dharma%20is%20a%20principle%20that%20divides%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%20Uprooting%20sanatana%20dharma%20is%20upholding%20humanity%20and%20human%20equality%2C%E2%80%9D%20Udhayanidhi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20prepared%20to%20confront%20any%20challenges%20that%20come%20my%20way%2C%20whether%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law%20or%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20court.%20Stop%20spreading%20fake%20news%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued%20to%20say%2C%20before%20adding%20that%20sanatana%20dharma%20was%20%E2%80%9Cresponsible%20for%20many%20evils%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsouth-india-final-frontier-contest-hinduism-hindutva%5C%22%3ESouth%20India%20Is%20the%20Final%20Frontier%20in%20the%20Contest%20Between%20Hinduism%20and%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20minister%20had%20elaborated%20on%20his%20ideological%20challenge%20to%20sanatana%20dharma%20in%20the%20very%20speech%20that%20the%20BJP%20picked%20up%20for%20its%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20sanatanam%3F%20The%20very%20name%20is%20from%20Sanskrit.%20Sanatana%20is%20against%20equality%20and%20social%20justice%20and%20nothing%20else.%20What%20is%20the%20meaning%20of%20sanatana%3F%20It%20is%20eternal%2C%20that%20is%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20changed%3B%20no%20one%20could%20pose%20any%20question%20and%20that%20is%20the%20meaning%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fsanatana-dharma-row-exposes-bjps-disconnect-one-election-chanters-who-dont-know-india%2Fcid%2F1963566%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUdhayanidhi%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20did%20sanatana%20do%20to%20women%3F%20It%20pushed%20women%2C%20who%20lost%20their%20husbands%2C%20into%20the%20fire%20%5Bthe%20erstwhile%20practice%20of%20sati%5D%3B%20it%20tonsured%20the%20heads%20of%20widows%20and%20made%20them%20wear%20white%20saris%3B%20child%20marriages%20too%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUdhayanidhi%20contrasted%20sanatana%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Crigidity%E2%80%9D%20with%20Dravidian%20ideology%2C%20which%20he%20said%20strived%20to%20establish%20equality%20and%20fraternity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekalaignar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bformer%20party%20leader%20Karunanidhi%5D%20brought%20a%20law%20enabling%20people%20belonging%20to%20all%20castes%20to%20become%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Earchakas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Btemple%20priests%5D%2C%20our%20chief%20minister%20%5BStalin%5D%20has%20appointed%20people%20who%20have%20completed%20archaka%20training%20as%20priests%20at%20temples%3B%20this%20is%20the%20Dravidian%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20Udhayanidhi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20did%20Dravidam%20%5Bthe%20Dravidian%20ideology%20followed%20by%20the%20DMK%5D%20do%3F%20It%20gave%20fare-free%20travel%20to%20women%20in%20buses%2C%20gave%20Rs%201%2C000%20monthly%20assistance%20to%20girl%20students%20for%20their%20college%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20war%20of%20words%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20has%20refused%20to%20back%20down%2C%20intensifying%20his%20attack%20on%20sanatana%20dharma%20and%20the%20alleged%20discrimination%20embedded%20within%20its%20doctrines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20matter%20has%20become%20yet%20another%20polarising%20political%20issue%2C%20the%20disagreements%20between%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalist%20politics%20and%20Dravidian%20ideology%20go%20back%20far%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanatanism%3A%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20view%20contrasts%20with%20the%20Hindutva%20groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncsc.nic.in%2Ffiles%2Freview%2520proforma%2Fselected%2520work%2520of%2520Dr%2520B%2520Rambedkar.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatana%20dharma%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eoften%20credited%20for%20defining%20the%20caste%20system%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20India%2C%20allocating%20duties%2C%20occupations%20and%20roles%20to%20communities.%20Critics%20say%20that%20sanatana%20practices%20speak%20about%20eternal%20laws%20but%20in%20effect%20have%20institutionalised%20discriminatory%20caste%20practices%20and%20sustained%20brahminical%20hegemony%20in%20Hindu%20society.%20For%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20Sanatanism%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cancient%20name%20for%20militant%20orthodox%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D.%20In%201943%2C%20he%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Antisemitism%20of%20the%20Nazis%20against%20the%20Jews%20is%20in%20no%20way%20different%20in%20ideology%20and%20in%20effect%20from%20the%20Sanatanism%20of%20the%20Hindus%20against%20the%20Untouchables.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20orgnisations%20have%20invoked%20sanatana%20dharma%20to%20standardise%20Hindu%20identity%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20often%20ignoring%20the%20diverse%20religious%20practices%20across%20India.%20Anti-caste%20organisations%20have%20naturally%20opposed%20such%20standardisation%20by%20Hindutva%20forces%20and%20have%20critiqued%20it%20for%20perpetuating%20casteism%20in%20the%20modern%20era.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Findia-culture-hindutva%5C%22%3EWhat%20Explains%20the%20Indian%20Desire%20for%20Homogenisation%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20may%20have%20interpreted%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20according%20to%20its%20own%20political%20convenience%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20opened%20a%20pandora%E2%80%99s%20box.%20The%20saffron%20party%20that%20was%20often%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9CBrahmin-Bania%E2%80%9D%20party%20for%20a%20long%20time%20has%20made%20concerted%20attempts%20to%20shed%20this%20tag%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20and%20anti-caste%20politics%20have%20historically%20remained%20inimical%20to%20each%20other.%20The%20perception%20that%20Hindutva%20is%20inherently%20brahminical%20and%20discriminatory%20had%20kept%20the%20Dravidian%2C%20Ambedkarite%20and%20Mandal%20parties%20away%20from%20the%20saffron%20umbrella%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Modi%20weaved%20a%20political%20narrative%20around%20nationalism%20and%20development%20that%20could%20supersede%20these%20contradictions.%20The%20BJP%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Modi%20has%20taken%20care%20not%20to%20run%20into%20these%20contradictions%20in%20the%20political%20sphere%2C%20choosing%20to%20popularise%20Hindutva%20by%20mostly%20fuelling%20anti-Muslim%20sentiment%20than%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20recent%20victories%20have%20been%20attributed%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20successful%20attempts%20to%20win%20over%20a%20substantial%20section%20of%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20communities%2C%20for%20whom%20caste%20discrimination%20has%20been%20a%20lived%20reality.%20By%20intensifying%20its%20attack%20on%20Udhayanidhi%2C%20who%20spoke%20against%20the%20inherent%20casteism%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20risk%20giving%20inadvertent%20prominence%20to%20the%20social%20justice%20rhetoric%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2FPluralist-vision-triumphs-in-Bihar%2Farticle59784595.ece%5C%22%3Etrumped%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%20multiple%20times%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20291px)%2085vw%2C%20291px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2-291x300.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22291%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2-291x300.jpeg%20291w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2-992x1024.jpeg%20992w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09101606%2FFqtn1praAAAjfU2.jpeg%201163w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-643324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20chief%20K.%20Annamalai.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40annamalai_k%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrecisely%20because%20of%20such%20possibilities%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20has%20refused%20to%20back%20down%20against%20persistent%20attacks%20by%20BJP%20leaders.%20Against%20such%20a%20backdrop%2C%20the%20most%20interesting%20response%20has%20been%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20president%20K.%20Annamalai.%20Unlike%20Malviya%20and%20Shah%2C%20Annamalai%20was%20much%20more%20cautious%20in%20attacking%20Udhayanidhi%2C%20carefully%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYPcZJWjXOVc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echoosing%20his%20words%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20saying%20that%20sanatana%20dharma%20was%20actually%20%E2%80%9Cmisinterpreted%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20DMK%20leader%20and%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20discriminatory%20as%20portrayed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnnamalai%20defended%20sanatana%20dharma%20as%20%E2%80%9Cegalitarian%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20what%20was%20a%20clear%20effort%20to%20downplay%20its%20perceived%20equivalence%20with%20brahaminical%20hegemony%20in%20southern%20states.%20He%20didn%E2%80%99t%20portray%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20as%20a%20call%20for%20a%20genocide%20like%20the%20national%20BJP%20leaders%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20aiming%20to%20gain%20a%20foothold%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20its%20state%20president%20well%20knows%20that%20any%20overt%20Hindutva%20messaging%20can%20only%20be%20detrimental%20to%20its%20prospects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-history%2Fsanatan-dharm-meaning-history-8924036%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20given%20its%20shape%20by%20the%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20in%20the%2019th%20century%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20a%20movement%20against%20reformist%20organisations%20like%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20and%20the%20Brahmo%20Samaj%2C%20which%20questioned%20regressive%20practices%20such%20as%20sati%2C%20idol%20worship%20and%20child%20marriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%20formed%20organisations%20like%20the%20Bharat%20Dharma%20Mahamandal%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatana%20Dharma%20Rakshini%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Lahore%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20Sabha%20to%20contain%20the%20growing%20influence%20of%20reformist%20organisations.%20These%20groups%20mostly%20attempted%20to%20homogenise%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20standardise%20%E2%80%93%20Hindu%20identity%20according%20to%20the%20doctrines%20of%20sanatana%20dharma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20have%20since%20then%20looked%20up%20to%20these%20groups%20as%20mentors%2C%20and%20their%20present%20advocacy%20of%20Hindu%20practices%20resembles%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%2019th-century%20Hindu%20orthodoxy%2C%20despite%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EModi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20political%20outreach%20among%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReformist%20organisations%20like%20the%20Arya%20Samaj%20and%20Radha%20Soamis%2C%20or%20even%20the%20Ramakrishna%20Mission%2C%20have%20evolved%20into%20different%20entities%20from%20their%2019th-century%20past.%20The%20contradictions%20between%20the%20orthodoxy%20and%20these%20groups%20have%20flattened%20out%20increasingly%20in%20the%20contemporary%20era%2C%20with%20many%20of%20these%20organisations%20finding%20themselves%20closer%20to%20the%20BJP%20than%20any%20other%20party.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20if%20the%20BJP%20persists%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20standardise%20Hindu%20identity%20by%20emphasising%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20the%20historical%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20may%20again%20become%20significant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%2019th-century%20social%20reformers%20like%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20and%20Narayana%20Guru%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20are%20frequently%20invoked%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eparivar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20messengers%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20spoke%20and%20acted%20aggressively%20against%20casteist%20practices%20in%20sanatana%20doctrines%20%E2%80%93%20exactly%20what%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%20hinged%20upon.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20author%20of%20the%20recently%20released%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVivekananda%3A%20The%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Govind%20Krishnan%20V.%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CVivekananda%20considered%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20oppression%20of%20the%20Kshatriyas%20and%20Brahmins%20over%20the%20so-called%20lower%20castes%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20decline%20and%20downfall%20from%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20civilisations%20of%20the%20world.%20In%20a%20series%20of%20speeches%20delivered%20in%20South%20India%20after%20his%20return%20from%20the%20West%2C%20Vivekananda%20called%20for%20the%20destruction%20of%20all%20caste%20privileges%20and%20of%20untouchability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fvivekananda-dismissed-hindutva-view-that-blames-foreign-invasions-for-indias-civilisational-decline%5C%22%3EVivekananda%20Dismissed%20Hindutva%20View%20That%20Blames%20Foreign%20Invasions%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20Civilisational%20Decline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20had%20a%20huge%20influence%20on%20the%20first%20non-party%20mass%20movement%20against%20caste%2C%20the%20Ezhava%20movement%20in%20Kerala.%20There%20is%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20similarity%20between%20Narayana%20Guru%20and%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20caste%2C%20especially%20since%20they%20were%20both%20vedantists.%20Vivekananda%20seemed%20to%20believe%20that%20caste%20will%20eventually%20disappear%20from%20India.%20He%20says%20caste%20distinctions%20are%20an%20obstacle%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20progress%20and%20would%20eventually%20disappear%20as%20democratic%20ideas%20advance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20casteist%20practices%20have%20anything%20but%20disappeared%20and%20remain%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20even%20present-day%20India%20in%20its%20society%20and%20its%20politics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EUdhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20have%20gone%20ahead%20and%20drawn%20the%20spotlight%20back%20on%20the%20seminal%20issue%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20historical%20reason%20for%20oppression%2C%20violence%20and%20deprivation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20appears%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20persistent%20attack%20on%20the%20Dravidian%20leader%20was%20also%20forced%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20unveiled%20a%20book%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERSS%E2%80%99s%20Role%20in%20the%20Indian%20Liberation%20War%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20same%20Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conference.%20The%20book%20highlighted%20the%20assassination%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20man%20licking%20a%20shoe%20in%20its%20cover.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pages%20inside%20were%20blank%20entirely%2C%20where%20Udhayanidhi%20drew%20three%20big%20zeroes%2C%20pointing%20towards%20the%20minimal%20role%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20struggle%20against%20the%20British.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDuring%20the%20%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conference%E2%80%99%20yesterday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUdhaystalin%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Udhaystalin%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20unveiled%20a%20book%20titled%20%E2%80%98RSS%E2%80%99s%20Role%20in%20the%20Indian%20Liberation%20War%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20page%20depicted%20someone%20licking%20a%20shoe%2C%20while%20the%20second%20page%20showcased%20the%20assassination%20of%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20pages%20were%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzNq77jYxja%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzNq77jYxja%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Siddharth%20(%40DearthOfSid)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDearthOfSid%2Fstatus%2F1698329219238134196%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20faultlines%20around%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99s%20proponents%20and%20opponents%20have%20come%20to%20a%20flashpoint%20in%20Batod%2C%20illustrating%20how%20disputes%20continue%20to%20prevail%20in%20even%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%20%E2%80%93%20a%20laboratory%20of%20Hindutva.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdeshgujarat.com%2F2023%2F09%2F01%2Fdistortion-of-hanuman-ji-its-vadtal-swaminarayan-sect-vs-all-other-sadhus-in-gujarat%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20say%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20a%20mural%20placed%20on%20the%20base%20of%20the%20largest%20statue%20of%20Hanumanji%20in%20Salangpur%20by%20the%20Swaminarayan%20sect%20is%20intensifying%20and%20the%20media%20has%20been%20barred%20from%20visiting%20the%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3