0on%20board.%20Often%2C%20they%20own%20properties%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20other%20assets%20in%20a%20range%20of%20countries%20that%20superyachts%20enable%20them%20seamless%20access%20to.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2212686190635_8b47dfabbc_c%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f5f5641b7ced0019c7cd20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20superyacht%20of%20Hollywood%20billionaire%20David%20Geffen.%3Cp%3EFlickr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20talking%20about%20what%20you%20would%20call%20'celebrities.'%20This%20is%20a%20different%20wealth%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20source%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20zeros%26quot%3B%20of%20difference%20between%20that%20of%20superyacht%20owners%20and%20their%20famous%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrokering%20deals%20in%20board%20shorts%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20board%20the%20vessels%2C%20the%20super%20rich%20and%20their%20celebrity%20friends%20can%20enjoy%20a%20level%20of%20privacy%2C%20peace%2C%20and%20seclusion%20they%20rarely%20have%20on%20dry%20land%20where%20they%20face%20pervasive%20media%20scrutiny.%20But%20the%20vessels%20are%20also%20places%20to%20impress%2C%20strengthen%20contacts%2C%20and%20broker%20deals%2C%20with%20the%20informal%20atmosphere%20offering%20unique%20opportunities%20to%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20fabulous%20guest%20%E2%80%94%20west%20coast%20American%20family%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20quite%20a%20bit%20more%20talkative%20than%20a%20multi-generational%20European%20wealth%20family%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20talking%20about%20the%20boats%2C%20and%20how%20much%20it%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%20of%20the%20vessel%2C%20the%20source%20said%2C%20revealed%20that%20such%20is%20a%20deal-making%20power%20of%20the%20yachts%20that%20in%20%26quot%3Bone%20year%20on%20board%2C%20it%20would%20pay%20for%20the%20boat.%20It's%20very%20hard%20to%20say%20'no'%20when%20you've%20been%20on%20board%20for%20a%20week%20and%20your%20family's%20been%20looked%20after%20so%20incredibly%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22865%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Superyacht%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f5faae1b7ced0019c7cf01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20woman%20poses%20in%20front%20of%20a%20yacht%20at%20the%20Hercules%20Port%20in%20Monaco%20on%20September%2027%2C%202017%20during%20the%2026th%20edition%20of%20the%20International%20Monaco%20Yacht%20Show.%3Cp%3EVALERY%20HACHE%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20trip%2C%20the%20source%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20at%20two%20absolute%20%5Bbusiness%5D%20titans%2C%20and%20you'd%20be%20amazed%20that%20they're%20sitting%20next%20to%20each%20other%20in%20board%20shorts%20and%20skanky%20T-shirts%20covered%20in%20salt%20having%20a%20cup%20of%20tea.%20And%20you're%20thinking%20the%20deal%20might%20not%20be%20struck%20today%2C%20but%20the%20next%20time%20they're%20on%20the%20phone%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20very%2C%20very%20different%20mood%20in%20the%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20other%20owners%2C%20the%20vessels%20offer%20the%20opportunity%20to%20escape%20the%20persona%20and%20pressures%20of%20their%20professional%20lives.%20He%20described%20one%20business%20leader%20accustomed%20to%20people%20%26quot%3Bkowtowing%26quot%3B%20him%20all%20day%20getting%20mercilessly%20ribbed%20by%20old%20school%20friends%20he%20invited%20on%20a%20trip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20on%20the%20main%20deck%20and%20his%20mates%20from%20childhood%20would%20be%20calling%20in%20every%20name%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20making%20fun%20of%20him.%20And%20that%2C%20I%20think%2C%20that's%20the%20value%20he%20got%20from%20his%20boat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20vast%20wealth%20comes%20high%20demands%20and%20tantrums.%20Superyacht%20owners%20can%20be%20intolerant%20of%20even%20the%20tiniest%20error%20or%20delay%2C%20the%20source%20said%2C%20and%20staff%20operate%20to%20precise%20schedules.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20they%20react%20because%20they've%20been%20waiting%20three%20and%20a%20half%20minutes%3F%20They%20do%20%E2%80%94%20really%20badly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20guests%20lucky%20enough%20to%20be%20invited%20on%20superyachts%20must%20also%20navigate%20a%20maze%20of%20etiquette%20to%20gel%20with%20their%20hosts%20and%20other%20guests.%20But%20some%20are%20so%20desperate%20to%20impress%20their%20wealthy%20hosts%20that%20the%20results%20can%20be%20excruciating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20do%20get%20your%20'try%20hards%2C'%20and%20it's%20just%20like%20'oh%20no%2C%20this%20is%20socially%20awkward%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReally%20the%20story%20of%20the%20day%20is%20about%20the%20kids%20playing%20in%20the%20water%2C%20and%20someone's%20trying%20to%20pitch.%20I've%20seen%20it%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20walked%20away%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20they%20misread%20the%20room.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22897%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f5f90b1b7ced0019c7ce84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESurveillance%20drones%20are%20being%20deployed%20to%20monitor%20superyachts.%3Cp%3EBruce%20Bennett%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpy%20drones%20and%20bugging%20devices%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20embarrassing%20guests%20are%20far%20from%20the%20only%20problem%20superyacht%20owners%20face.%20The%20privacy%20of%20the%20vessels%2C%20and%20the%20wealth%2C%20fame%2C%20and%20power%20of%20their%20owners%20and%20passengers%20inevitably%20draw%20unwelcome%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimon%20Rowland%20is%20a%20former%20UK%20Royal%20Marines%20soldier%20whose%20company%2C%20Veritas%2C%20provides%20comprehensive%20security%20for%20superyachts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Insider%20that%20among%20the%20most%20frequent%20challenges%20he%20has%20to%20tackle%20is%20handling%20spy%20drones%20sent%20by%20news%20organizations%20to%20photograph%20the%20boats%20and%20their%20wealthy%20and%20famous%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrones%20are%20increasingly%20a%20concern%20for%20superyacht%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20saying%20tabloid%20news%20organizations%20and%20the%20superyacht%20press%20like%20to%20use%20the%20devices%20to%20get%20the%20%26quot%3Bmoney%20shot%26quot%3B%20and%20take%20overhead%20pictures%20of%20the%20boats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20some%20vessels%20deployed%20devices%20to%20scramble%20the%20navigation%20systems%20of%20drones%20and%20take%20them%20out%20of%20the%20air%2C%20but%20there%20were%20question%20marks%20over%20whether%20this%20is%20legal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20easier%20solution%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20an%20alarm%20system%20alerting%20passengers%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20drones%2C%20allowing%20them%20time%20to%20get%20off%20deck%20and%20away%20from%20invasive%20air-bourne%20camera%20lenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20drones%20aren't%20the%20only%20form%20of%20covert%20surveillance%20Rowlands%20has%20to%20be%20vigilant%20of.%20Spies%20could%20try%20to%20infiltrate%20superyachts%20through%20crew%20members%2C%20or%20through%20installing%20surveillance%20devices%2C%20to%20steal%20sensitive%20information%20on%20business%20deals%20or%20politics.%20A%20particular%20target%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20vessels%20known%20to%20be%20frequently%20chartered%20by%20the%20wealthy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20would%20expect%20a%20y