xperts%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20author%20specifies%20at%20the%20very%20beginning.%20Neither%20is%20it%20meant%20for%20students%20of%20advanced%20biology.%20It%20is%20a%20primer%20that%20distills%20decades%20of%20Nobel%20winning%20scientific%20achievements%20into%20a%20coherent%20series%20of%20cause%20and%20effect%20relationships%20that%20add%20up%20to%20the%20perfect%20whole%20for%20young%20people%2C%20still%20on%20the%20fence%20about%20what%20career%20to%20pursue%2C%20but%20curious%20about%20the%20big%20picture%20and%20saving%20the%20planet.%20The%20author%20attempts%20to%20take%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view%20of%20the%20vast%20and%20diverse%20system%20that%20is%20simplistically%20referred%20to%20as%20biology%2C%20presenting%20it%20as%20a%20vector%20sum%20of%20multiple%20societal%20and%20political%20determinants%20that%20constitute%20a%C2%A0%20larger%20system%20encompassing%20individuals%2C%20governments%2C%20corporations%2C%20admen%20and%20microorganisms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20407px)%2085vw%2C%20407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04184127%2F61wQa7z0NwL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22407%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04184127%2F61wQa7z0NwL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20647w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04184127%2F61wQa7z0NwL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-194x300.jpg%20194w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671421%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22629%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr%20K.Srinath%20Reddy.%20Pulse%20to%20Planet.%20Harper%20Collins%20(2023).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20my%20favourite%20paragraphs%20from%20the%20book%20covers%2C%20in%20one%20fell%20swoop%2C%20the%20wide%20expanse%20between%20embryology%20and%20epidemiology.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20foet