of%2030%20million%20visitors%20in%20the%20OTT%20market.%20This%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20players%2C%20as%20well%20as%20users%2C%20has%20further%20led%20companies%20to%20adopt%20innovative%20strategies%20to%20generate%20revenue%20which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20case%20earlier.%20Such%20innovative%20strategies%20by%20OTT%20platforms%20have%20recently%20become%20a%20subject%20matter%20of%20scrutiny%20where%20the%20platforms%20are%20adopting%20various%20methods%20to%20maintain%20a%20competitive%20edge%20in%20the%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPricing%20Mechanism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20platforms%20have%20had%20to%20adjust%20their%20subscription%20fee%20to%20their%20revenue%20costs%20which%20has%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20their%20pricing%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20For%20instance%2C%20Hotstar%20recently%20increased%20its%20monthly%20subscription%20fee%20from%20Rs%20199%20to%20Rs%20299%2C%20while%20SonyLIV%20has%20increased%20it%20from%20Rs%2099%20to%20Rs%20299.%20Netflix%20being%20an%20established%20player%20in%20the%20market%20has%20been%20able%20to%20maintain%20its%20monthly%20subscription%20rate%20costing%20Rs%20499.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20median%20annual%20subscription%20fee%20for%20the%20top%20seven%20OTT%20players%20in%20the%20market%20comes%20out%20as%20Rs%20999.%20This%20amount%20is%20quite%20high%20given%20that%20the%20market%20is%20in%20its%20nascent%20stage%2C%20with%20no%20established%20loyalties%20among%20its%20subscriber%20base%20and%20a%20high%20subscriber%20attrition%20rate.%20So%20the%20players%20are%20effectively%20fighting%20for%20a%20share%20in%20an%20extremely%20volatile%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20%E2%80%98free-ride%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20this%20fight%20for%20market%20expansion%20and%20revenue%20maximisation%2C%20Jiocinema%20introduced%20yet%20another%20factor%20in%20the%20market%20which%20was%20previously%20absent.%20The%20company%20chose%20to%20stream%20IPL%20matches%20on%20its%20website%20for%20free%2C%20even%20though%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrandequity.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fmedia%2Fdisney-bets-on-free-mobile-cricket-streaming-in-india-in-battle-with-jiocinema%2F100891136%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espent%20%242.9%20bn%20on%20buying%20IPL%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20telecasting%20rights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20.%20The%20gains%20were%20apparent%20%E2%80%93%20even%20though%20the%20company%20lost%20on%20subscription%20revenues%2C%20it%20got%20access%20to%20millions%20of%20users%E2%80%99%20attention%20which%20was%20ultimately%20monetised%20through%20the%20sale%20of%20advertisements.%20The%20free-ride%20given%20by%20JioCinema%20has%20already%20started%20hurting%20the%20competitors%20in%20the%20market%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F05%2F10%2Fdisney-hotstar-loses-8-4-million-subscribers-as-ambani-jiocinema-takes-off%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHotstar%252C%2520which%2520counts%2520India%2520as%2CDisney%2520extend%2520beyond%2520subscriber%2520attrition.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHotstar%20facing%20a%20loss%20of%208.4%20million%20subscribers%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Esince%20October%2C%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20forcing%20it%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F06%2F09%2Fdisney-hotstar-free-mobile-cricket-streaming-jiocinema%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecalibrate%20its%20strategy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20mention%20that%20YouTube%20has%20been%20offering%20free%20content%20since%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20and%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20Jiocinema%20may%20only%20be%20a%20follower.%20The%20platform%20is%20known%20to%20generate%20revenues%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20advertisements.%20It%20was%20recently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fyoutube-s-short-and-smart-future-here-re-challenges-opportunities-123061800974_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20company%20is%20planning%20to%20propel%20its%20growth%20on%20free%20content%20through%20short%20videos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20may%20be%20attractive%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20no%20upfront%20costs%20for%20the%20consumers%20to%20bear%20at%20the%20surface%20level%2C%20a%20closer%20look%20would%20suggest%20otherwise%2C%20which%20is%20best%20explained%20with%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98if%20you%20are%20not%20paying%20for%20the%20product%2C%20then%20you%20are%20the%20product%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYouTube%E2%80%99s%20parent%20group%2C%20i.e.%20Google%20Inc.%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20providing%20unauthorised%20access%20of%20user%20information%20to%20advertisers%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20multiple%20scrutinies.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20found%20violating%20competition%20laws%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20has%20lately%20entered%20a%20grey%20area%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20data%20protection%20as%20well.%20Australian%20Competition%20and%20Consumer%20Commission%20(ACCC)%20further%20suggested%20that%20the%20lawmaker%20may%20need%20to%20come%20up%20with%20new%20legislation%20to%20address%20the%20harms%20caused%20by%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20in%20the%20Ad-Tech%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMatch%20streaming%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Relevant%20Market%20%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFree%20live%20streaming%20of%20sports%20services%20may%20further%20suggest%20it%20as%20a%20separate%20relevant%20market%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20promoting%20competition.%20The%20Indian%20competition%20commission%2C%20though%20in%20a%20different%20set%20of%20facts%20and%20circumstances%2C%20held%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cci.gov.in%2Fantitrust%2Forders%2Fdetails%2F760%2F0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecricket%20matches%20cannot%20be%20substituted%20with%20other%20entertainment%20channels%20and%20movies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Therefore%2C%20viewers%20of%20live%20sports%20may%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20distinct%20category.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESustained%20growth%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20a%20market%20economics%20point%20of%20view%2C%20it%20remains%20imperative%20that%20the%20incumbents%20aren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20offer%20free%20services%20for%20long.%20This%20may%20be%20truer%20for%20entrenched%20players%20in%20the%20economy.%20Such%20a%20strategy%20has%20constantly%20invited%20scrutiny%20from%20competition%20bodies%20across%20the%20globe.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20India%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Reliance%20Jio%20with%20free-services%20was%20marred%20with%20multiple%20complaints.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20sector-based%20regulation%2C%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20such%20free%20services%20not%20only%20fall%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20predatory%20pricing%2C%20but%20also%20allow%20Reliance%20Industries%20as%20a%20group%20to%20fuel%20its%20entry%20in%20the%20telecom%20market%20through%20dominance%20in%20other%20relevant%20markets%20%E2%80%93%20both%20the%20practices%20prohibited%20under%20express%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Competition%20Act.%20Even%20though%20the%20telecom%20industry%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time%20was%20flourishing%20with%20multiple%20players%20in%20the%20market%2C%20Reliance%20Industries%E2%80%99%20deep%20pockets%20allowed%20it%20to%20fund%20its%20new%20service%20well%20beyond%20the%20prescribed%20time%20limit%2C%20thereby%20resulting%20in%20multiple%20exits%20of%20competing%20players%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20an%20apparent%20implication%20on%20the%20consumer-welfare%20standard.%20Promotion%20of%20such%20a%20standard%20has%20been%20a%20long-sought%20goal%20of%20various%20economic%20legislations%20and%20therefore%2C%20it%20becomes%20important%20for%20the%20government%20to%20conduct%20detailed%20stakeholder%20consultation%20so%20that%20economically%20efficient%20outcomes%20are%20achieved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20focus%20has%20been%20on%20regulating%20the%20content%20on%20such%20platforms%2C%20it%20may%20be%20high%20time%20for%20it%20to%20assess%20the%20market%20potential%20and%20subsequent%20competition%20concerns%20which%20may%20be%20arising%20out%20of%20it.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20nodal%20Indian%20competition%20regulator%20has%20been%20taking%20such%20industry-specific%20studies%20from%20time%20to%20time%20as%20part%20of%20its%20mandate.%20While%20the%20dynamic%20nature%20of%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20may%20require%20the%20government%20to%20periodically%20review%20its%20position%20while%20regulating%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20%E2%80%98free%E2%80%99%20services%2C%20irrespective%20of%20live%20streaming%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20separate%20RM%2C%20warrants%20a%20second%20look%20especially%20when%20offered%20by%20industry%20giants.%20A%20thorough%20review%20of%20the%20sector%20is%20required%C2%A0given%20that%20until%20now%20the%20model%20has%20been%20that%20of%20charging%20a%20subscription%20fee%20for%20the%20services%20provided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20OTT%20market%20is%20in%20a%20growing%20phase.%20While%20there%20may%20be%20immense%20potential%20in%20the%20market%20to%20be%20explored%2C%20price%20warfare%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20brewing%20maturity%2C%20has%20already%20begun.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20digital%20markets%2C%20regulations%20should%20follow%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20industry%20rather%20than%20trailing%20behind.%20In%20the%20world%20of%20ex-ante%20regulations%2C%20Indian%20regulators%20should%20invest%20time%20and%20resources%20in%20conducting%20research%20and%20study%20on%20digital%20markets%20and%20engaging%20with%20all%20the%20relevant%20stakeholders%20before%20arriving%20at%20any%20policy%20decision..%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20larger%20goal%20should%20be%20to%20make%20economically%20efficient%20law%20and%20policies%20in%20the%20betterment%20of%20consumers%20without%20warping%20the%20market%20principles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESumit%20Jain%20is%20a%20director%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Competition%20Law%20and%20Economics%20and%20Abhishek%20Raj%20is%20a%20consultant%20at%20the%20CCLE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693831824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F20124618%2Fnetflix.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fregulating-otts-in-india-the-government-needs-to-shift-its-focus-from-content-to-economics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20it%20comes%20to%20digital%20markets%2C%20regulations%20should%20follow%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20industry%20rather%20than%20trailing%20behind.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fregulating-otts-in-india-the-government-needs-to-shift-its-focus-from-content-to-economics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israelis%20held%20in%20Cyprus%20over%20alleged%20rape%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693831040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FB8E0%2Fproduction%2F_130982374_aiyanapagettyimages-1234572141.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20foreign%20ministry%20says%20six%20citizens%20were%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20raping%20a%20British%20tourist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A106%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fresh%20Adani%20Revelations%20that%20Hint%20at%20Regulator%20SEBI%20Inaction%20Could%20Hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20FATF%20Credibility%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F21181904%2Fadani-brothers.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20(FATF)%20review%20of%20India%20currently%20underway%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20signals%20emanating%20from%20the%20kid%20glove%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20by%20various%20investigative%20agencies%20and%20market%20watchdog%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inability%20or%20unwillingness%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20serious%20charges%20of%20round%20tripping%20or%20the%20flow%20of%20money%20from%20and%20to%20tax%20havens%20allegedly%20around%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20and%20fastest%20growing%20conglomerate%20could%20have%20a%20series%20of%20unintended%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20consequence%20could%20be%20a%20shadow%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20integrity%20as%20a%20responsible%20system%20having%20institutional%20heft%20to%20know%20about%2C%20and%20prevent%2C%20illegal%20flows%20of%20money%20across%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FATF%20is%20the%20global%20money%20laundering%20and%20terrorist%20financing%20watchdog.%20According%20to%20its%20own%20definition%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Csets%20international%20standards%20that%20aim%20to%20prevent%20these%20illegal%20activities%20and%20the%20harm%20they%20cause%20to%20society%E2%80%9D.%20North%20Korea%2C%20Iran%20and%20Myanmar%20are%20currently%20on%20the%20FATF%20black%20list.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20October%202022%20that%20Pakistan%20after%20four%20years%20of%20finding%20itself%20on%20the%20grey%20list%20and%20facing%20serious%20financial%20strictures%2C%20could%20manage%20to%20make%20its%20way%20off%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20SEBI%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20alleged%20stock%20price%20manipulation%20in%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20at%20least%20one%20investigation%20was%20contingent%20on%20receiving%20crucial%20data%20from%20overseas%2C%20pending%20which%20it%20cannot%20go%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20submission%20will%20hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20case%20as%20this%20is%20a%20direct%20violation%20of%20Outcome%20number%20two%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fatf-gafi.org%2Fen%2Fpublications%2FMutualevaluations%2FFatf-methodology.html%5C%22%3EFATF%20guidelines.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20telling%20the%20court%20that%20it%20is%20awaiting%20information%20from%20overseas%2C%20SEBI%20is%20essentially%20admitting%20that%20a%20robust%20international%20cooperation%20is%20lacking%2C%20which%20is%20what%20Outcome%202%20is%20all%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22To%20Legalise%20Power%20Project%20Given%20to%20Adani%20Without%20Tender%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Wants%20it%20Turned%20Into%20Govt-to-Govt%20Deal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fto-legalise-power-project-given-to-adani-without-tender-sri-lanka-wants-it-turned-into-govt-to-govt-deal%5C%22%3ETo%20Legalise%20Power%20Project%20Given%20to%20Adani%20Without%20Tender%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Wants%20it%20Turned%20Into%20Govt-to-Govt%20Deal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FATF%20review%20by%20the%20UN%20body%20follows%2040%20recommendations%20and%2011%20outcomes%20while%20doing%20a%20country%20review.%20The%20recommendations%20are%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20robust%20laws%2C%20rules%20and%20regulations%20being%20in%20place%20and%20the%20outcome%20is%20about%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20implementing%20these%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20who%20are%20familiar%20with%20the%20workings%20of%20the%20FATF%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20incumbent%20on%20the%20country%20to%20get%20the%20information%20it%20is%20asking%20for%20because%20if%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20get%20the%20information%2C%20it%20means%20our%20request%20was%20not%20as%20per%20the%20law%20or%20was%20lacking%20in%20some%20way.%20The%20FATF%20looks%20at%20the%20broader%20prospective%20of%20international%20cooperation%20as%20well%20as%20robust%20domestic%20coordination.%20Our%20ratings%20are%20likely%20to%20fall%20on%20the%20domestic%20front%20as%20well.%20Weak%20coordination%20between%20various%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20no%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20by%20any%20federal%20or%20state%20agency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20had%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20August%2025%20that%20data%20from%20five%20offshore%20tax%20havens%20was%20awaited%20which%20will%20identify%20the%20end%20beneficiaries%20behind%20foreign%20investors%20who%20are%20engaged%20with%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20later%2C%20a%20report%20by%20a%20consortium%20of%20investigative%20reporters%2C%20from%20the%20OCCRP%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20asserted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20documents%20accessed%20by%20them%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20has%20invested%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20its%20own%20companies%20through%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20offshore%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20also%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20had%20alerted%20SEBI%20about%20suspicious%20transactions%20of%20these%20off%20shore%20entities%20as%20early%20as%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20SEBI%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20it%20had%20information%20coming%20in%20only%20as%20late%20as%202020%2C%20after%20which%20it%20started%20its%20enquiries.%20SEBI%20has%20been%20silent%20on%20if%20it%20has%20investigated%20the%20leads%20given%20to%20it%20by%20the%20DRI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%E2%80%99s%20actions%20or%20the%20lack%20of%20them%20impact%20Outcome%203%20and%204%20of%20FATF%20because%20of%20the%20failure%20of%20SEBI%20and%20RBI%20to%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20where%20funds%20for%20the%20Adani%20group%20are%20coming%20from.%20The%20RBI%20is%20supposed%20to%20maintain%20the%20balance%20of%20payments%20position.%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20role%20as%20the%20gatekeeper%20of%20%C2%A0the%20flow%20of%20money%20incoming%20and%20outgoing%20from%20India%20is%20also%20assessed%20during%20an%20FATF%20review.%20It%20too%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20raise%20questions%20about%20alleged%20illicit%20flow%20of%20money.%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20effectiveness%20is%20one%20of%20the%2011%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20the%20Black%20Money%20Was%20Brought%20Back%20to%20India%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fhow-the-black-money-was-brought-back-to-india%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Black%20Money%20Was%20Brought%20Back%20to%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20group%20has%20dubbed%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20as%20baseless%20and%20and%20the%20OCCRP%20findings%20as%20%E2%80%9Crecycled%20allegations%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3EJanuary%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20dubbed%20the%20Adani%20group%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20con%20in%20corporate%20history%E2%80%9D%20shaved%20off%20a%20%24100%20billion%20worth%20of%20the%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20various%20verticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediate%20outcome%207%20of%20FATF%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20impacted%20going%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fhindenburg-spotlights-an-offshore-adani-related-entity-that-ed-had-linked-to-agustawestland-scam%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Ethis%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20shows%20a%20failure%20of%20a%20domestic%20federal%20agency%2C%20or%20its%20inability%20to%20take%20a%20prosecution%20to%20a%20logical%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20in%20February%20this%20year%20reported%20that%20an%20Adani%20company%2C%20Gudami%20International%20Pte%20Ltd%2C%20had%20been%20one%20of%20the%20alleged%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Agusta%20Westland%20VVIP%20chopper%20deal%20slush%20funds.%20The%20company%20figured%20in%20two%20chargesheets%20filed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%202014%20and%202015%20where%20details%20of%20how%20the%20bribes%20were%20paid%20was%20shared.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20ED%20sent%20a%20Letter%20Rogatory%20to%20Singapore%20where%20Gudami%20International%20was%20registered.%20In%20the%20third%20chargesheet%2C%20while%20several%20other%20companies%20and%20the%20Singapore%20information%20were%20mentioned%2C%20Gudami%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COutcome%208%20too%20is%20impacted%20because%20since%20there%20is%20no%20conviction%20in%20this%20case%2C%20there%20is%20no%20confiscation%20of%20property%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Gudami%20International%20Pte%20Ltd%2C%E2%80%9D%20officials%20familiar%20with%20the%20case%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20anti%20money%20laundering%20agency%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20or%20ED%E2%80%99s%20not%20too%20stellar%20record%20also%20directly%20impacts%20Outcome%207%20and%208%20of%20the%20FATF.%20While%20Outcome%207%20deals%20with%20prosecution%20and%20convictions%2C%20Outcome%208%20deals%20with%20confiscation%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20its%20website%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20a%20conviction%20rate%20of%2096%25%2C%20politicians%20comprise%20only%203%25%20of%20all%20cases%20and%20search%20warrants%20were%20issued%20in%208.99%25%20of%20the%20cases.%20But%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98conviction%20rate%E2%80%99%20is%20based%20on%2024%20out%20of%2025%20cases%20in%20which%20a%20PMLA%20trial%20was%20completed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIANS%20quoting%20finance%20ministry%20sources%20reported%20that%20between%202018-19%20and%202021-22%2C%20cases%20registered%20by%20ED%20rose%20by%20505%25%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2F505-rise-in-cases-registered-by-ed-since-2018-1205886.html%5C%22%3Efrom%20195%20cases%20in%202018-19%2C%20to%201%2C180%20in%202021-22%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20number%20of%20searches%20the%20ED%20conducted%20rose%20by%20a%20huge%202%2C555%25%20between%202004-14%20and%202014-22.%20As%20per%20finance%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%2C%20112%20searches%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20ED%20between%202004-14%20resulting%20in%20attachment%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20worth%20Rs%205%2C346%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20gave%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0a%20three-page%20response%20to%20its%20queries%2C%20but%20some%20questions%20regarding%20the%20role%20of%20the%20agency%20remain%20unanswered%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20cases%20has%20the%20investigation%20been%20completed%20so%20trial%20can%20commence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20cases%20have%20been%20registered%20and%20closed%20by%20way%20of%20discharge%20or%20quashing%20or%20acquittal%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20accused%20have%20been%20discharged%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20filed%20in%20court%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20properties%20attached%2C%20how%20many%20have%20been%20confiscated%20by%20the%20ED%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20then%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tenor%20and%20content%20of%20your%20letter%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20based%20not%20only%20on%20incorrect%20and%20misleading%20facts%20but%20also%20shows%20that%20you%20have%20not%20conducted%20proper%20research%20including%20checking%20the%20website%20of%20the%20ED.%20Otherwise%2C%20you%20have%20not%20put%20certain%20questions%20relating%20to%20statistics%20and%20asked%20for%20answers%20from%20us.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20letter%20is%20to%20do%20a%20roving%20inquiry%20for%20an%20oblique%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ED%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsk-mishra-enforcement-directorate-fatf-evaluation%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20time%20that%20FATF%20was%20in%20the%20news%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20when%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20arguing%20for%20the%20retention%20of%20ED%20Director%2C%20Sanjay%20Mishra%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20stiff%20resistance%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20Modi%20government%20had%20repeatedly%20invoked%20the%20FATF%20review%20as%20crucial%20and%20underlined%20the%20role%20Mishra%20was%20playing%20in%20seeing%20India%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693830657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F21181904%2Fadani-brothers.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffresh-adani-revelations-that-hint-at-regulator-sebi-inaction-could-hurt-indias-fatf-credibility%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20review%20by%20the%20global%20money%20laundering%20and%20terrorist%20financing%20watchdog%20is%20underway%20and%20an%20impression%20that%20regulators%20are%20ignorant%20or%20unwilling%20to%20act%20on%20charges%20of%20illegal%20money%20flows%20could%20be%20detrimental%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20credibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A79%2C%22canonicalUrl%