%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0moment%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20August.%20Affected%20women%20from%20the%20world%20of%20chess%20rallied%20together%20to%20write%20an%20open%20letter%C2%A0demanding%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%C2%A0female%20chess%20players%2C%20coaches%2C%20referees%20and%20managers%20have%20experienced%20sexism%C2%A0or%20sexual%20violence%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20male%20chess%20players%2C%20coaches%2C%20referees%20or%20managers%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20read.%20It%20was%20signed%20by%20more%20than%20100%20women%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20is%20German%20national%20player%20Annmarie%20M%C3%BCtsch.%20She%20recently%20told%20German%20news%20magazine%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fder-spiegel-admits-star-reporter-falsified-stories-on-a-grand-scale%2Fa-46808277%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSpiegel%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20she%20had%20canceled%20her%20participation%20in%20important%20tournaments%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20certain%20people%20she%20would%20rather%20not%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04170212%2Fdw.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22German%20chess%20player%20Annmarie%20M%C3%BCtsch%20was%20among%20those%20who%20signed%20the%20open%20letter%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04170212%2Fdw.jpeg%201110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04170212%2Fdw-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04170212%2Fdw-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671405%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22624%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGerman%20chess%20player%20Annmarie%20M%C3%BCtsch%20was%20among%20those%20who%20signed%20the%20open%20letter.%20Credit%3A%20Paul%20Meyer-Dunker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20is%20chess%20particularly%20affected%20by%20sexism%3F%20Grandmaster%20and%20DSB%20spokesperson%20Josefine%20Heinemann%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20think%20so.%20%E2%80%9COf%20course%2C%20I%20have%20been%20hit%20on%20at%20a%20chess%20tournament%20before%20and%20maybe%20it%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20uncomfortable.%20But%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20classify%20that%20as%20sexual%20harassment%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Heinemann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESituations%20like%20those%20aren%E2%80%99t%20exclusive%20to%20the%20chess%20environment%2C%20she%20said%2C%20they%20are%20part%20of%20everyday%20life.%20It%20is%20a%20problem%20facing%20society%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreater%20danger%20beyond%20the%20board%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20one%20major%20difference%20in%20chess%3A%20Women%20are%20greatly%20in%20the%20minority%2C%20with%20only%2010%25%20of%20all%20players%20identifying%20as%20female.%20Women-only%20tournaments%20do%20exist%2C%20but%20if%20female%20players%20want%20to%20challenge%20themselves%20at%20the%20top%20level%2C%20they%20have%20to%20take%20part%20in%20mixed%20tournaments%20to%20advance%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20also%20unique%20to%20chess%C2%A0that%20younger%20women%20often%C2%A0compete%20face-to-face%20against%20older%20men%2C%20which%20can%20cause%20annoyance%20if%C2%A0the%20woman%20wins.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20often%20a%20comment%2C%20especially%20when%20older%20men%20lose%20to%20younger%20girls%2C%E2%80%9D%20Heinemann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grandmaster%2C%20however%2C%20sees%20an%20even%20greater%C2%A0danger%20beyond%20the%20chessboard.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20my%20point%20of%20view%2C%20there%20are%20already%20a%20lot%20of%20stupid%20comments%20on%20the%20internet.%20Some%20things%20I%20read%20on%20there%20leave%20me%20shocked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwhy-social-media-can-be-a-double-edged-sword-for-athletes%2Fa-60874573%5C%22%3Eprovides%20anonymity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20inhibition%20threshold%20falls%20drastically.%20Lauterbach%20also%20believes%20that%20modern%20communication%20channels%20and%20chess%20websites%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20communicate%20with%20people%20against%20their%20will.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20internet%20also%20provides%20a%20platform%20for%20those%20affected%20by%20sexism%20to%20fight%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShahade%20as%20the%20pioneer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20no%20longer%20want%20to%20stay%20silent.%20In%20February%2C%20two%20times%20US%20champion%20and%20influential%20chess%20writer%20Jennifer%20Shahade%20posted%20on%20what%20was%20then%20called%20Twitter%2C%20but%20is%20now%20known%20as%20X%3A%20%E2%80%9CTime%E2%80%99s%20up.%E2%80%9D%20In%20her%20post%2C%20she%20described%20the%20sexual%20misconduct%20she%20had%20allegedly%20experienced%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20chess%20grandmaster%20Alejandro%20Ramirez.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ETime%E2%80%99s%20up.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FItOv73lTX7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FItOv73lTX7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jennifer%20Shahade%20(%40JenShahade)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJenShahade%2Fstatus%2F1625873098581983232%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20minutes%2C%20many%20people%20commented%2C%20detailing%20similar%20experiences%20in%20the%20past.%20Among%20them%20was%20a%20man%C2%A0who%20confessed%20he%20had%20witnessed%20Ramirez%20allegedly%20assaulting%20a%20young%20woman%20in%202011%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20was%20an%20issue%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20that%20time%2C%20various%20abuse%20scandals%20had%20already%20caused%20uproar%20worldwide.%20So%20how%20did%20no%20one%20seemingly%20notice%20anything%20in%20chess%3F%20Ramirez%20says%20he%20is%20cooperating%20with%20various%20investigations%20and%20looks%20forward%20to%20giving%20his%20side%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWere%20such%20allegations%C2%A0just%20all%20too%20common%20in%20the%20past%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20German%20player%20M%C3%BCtsch%3A%20%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20signed%20the%20open%20letter%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20thought%20more%20about%20the%20incidents%20I%E2%80%99ve%20experienced.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20thought%20of%20so%20many%20things%20that%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20aware%20of%20before.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20clear%20point%20of%20contact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican-Canadian%20chess%20player%20and%20influencer%20Alexandra%20Valeria%20Botez%20set%20up%20an%20initiative%20for%20an%20anonymous%2C%20international%20database%20to%20collect%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20in%20chess%20worldwide.%20A%20reaction%20she%20deemed%20necessary%2C%20as%20no%20major%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-chess-federations-swiss-accounts-frozen-over-presidents-syria-sanctions%2Fa-42593833%5C%22%3EWorld%20Chess%20Federation%20(FIDE)%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20except%20for%C2%A0the%20Ethics%20Commission%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20of%20contact%20for%20those%20affected%20by%20sexual%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04170125%2F66681840_906.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ingrid%20Lauterbach%20is%20president%20of%20the%20German%20Chess%20Federation%20(DSB)%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%2