20company.%20In%20moving%20forward%20with%20the%20project%2C%20they%20risked%20a%20defamation%20or%20publicity%20suit%20by%20Zuckerberg%20and%20others%20depicted%20in%20the%20film.%20But%20their%20gamble%20paid%20off%3A%20Zuckerberg%2C%20while%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fperma.cc%2FSN4H-UXAP%5C%22%3Ecritical%20of%20his%20depiction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20sue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20other%20subjects%20who%20have%20been%20depicted%20in%20dramatic%20features%20without%20their%20authorisation%20have%20sued%20to%20recover%20a%20share%20of%20the%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESilver%20screen%20legend%20Olivia%20de%20Havilland%2C%20for%20example%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasetext.com%2Fcase%2Fde-havilland-v-fx-networks-llc-1%5C%22%3Esued%20FX%20Studios%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20briefly%20depicting%20her%20in%20a%20miniseries%20about%20Hollywood%20rivals%20Bette%20Davis%20and%20Joan%20Crawford.%20She%20won%20at%20trial%2C%20though%20an%20appeals%20court%20reversed%20her%20victory%2C%20citing%20the%20producers%E2%80%99%20First%20Amendment%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawsuits%20can%20even%20be%20brought%20when%20the%20characters%E2%80%99%20names%20and%20story%20details%20have%20been%20changed.%20US%20Army%20Sgt.%20Jeffrey%20Sarver%2C%20the%20bomb-defusing%20expert%20who%20inspired%20the%20Oscar-winning%20film%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt0887912%2F%3Fref_%3Dnv_sr_srsg_0_tt_8_nm_0_q_the%252520hurt%252520locker%5C%22%3EThe%20Hurt%20Locker%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasetext.com%2Fcase%2Fsarver-v-chartier%5C%22%3Esued%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20producers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20violating%20his%20right%20of%20publicity.%20He%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawsuits%20like%20these%20are%20not%20the%20norm.%20But%20many%20producers%20hope%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20a%20flimsy%20lawsuit%20and%20bad%20publicity%20by%20acquiring%20nonexistent%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20is%20in%20the%20public%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Edomain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20and%20much%20that%20is%20right%20%E2%80%93%20with%20paying%20individuals%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20production%20of%20features%20about%20themselves.%20Doing%20so%20can%20convey%20respect%20toward%20the%20subject%20and%20make%20the%20production%20go%20more%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20that%20life%20story%20acquisitions%20have%20entered%20the%20popular%20consciousness%20has%20spurred%20the%20widespread%20belief%20that%20any%20portrayal%20of%20a%20factual%20series%20of%20events%20entitles%20those%20depicted%20to%20a%20lucrative%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20expectation%20increases%20production%20costs%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20litigation%2C%20thereby%20deterring%20otherwise%20worthwhile%20projects%20and%20depriving%20the%20public%20of%20meaningful%20content%20that%20is%20based%20on%20true%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20be%20done%20about%20this%20situation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20idea%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4480628%5C%22%3Ethat%20we%E2%80%99ve%20written%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0would%20prevent%20right%20of%20publicity%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20the%20basis%20for%20many%20life%20story%20lawsuits%20%E2%80%93%20from%20being%20used%20against%20works%20that%20convey%20ideas%20and%20tell%20a%20story%2C%20such%20as%20books%2C%20films%20and%20TV%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20that%20can%20be%20done%2C%20though%2C%20is%20educating%20people%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20right%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20every%20description%20of%20the%20events%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollective%20history%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20belongs%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJorge%20L.%20Contreras%2C%20James%20T.%20Jensen%20Endowed%20Professor%20for%20Transactional%20Law%20and%20Director%2C%20Program%20on%20Intellectual%20Property%20and%20Technology%20Law%2C%20University%20of%20Utah%3B%20and%20Dave%20Fagundes%2C%20Baker%20Botts%20LLP%20Professor%20of%20Law%20and%20Research%20Dean%2C%20University%20of%20Houston%20Law%20Center.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fmichael-oher-mike-tyson-and-the-question-of-whether-you-own-your-life-story-212242%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693824313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04154720%2FMike-Tyson.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fcan-you-own-your-life-story%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Life%20story%20acquisitions%E2%80%99%20have%20led%20to%20the%20belief%20that%20any%20portrayal%20of%20a%20factual%20series%20of%20events%20entitles%20those%20depicted%20to%20a%20lucrative%20payday.%20But%20is%20this%20true%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fcan-you-own-your-life-story%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dogs%20perform%20Mozart%20with%20orchestra%20in%20Denmark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FBEA8%2Fproduction%2F_130980884_p0gbkxtn.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66705222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20dogs%20participated%20in%20a%20performance%20of%20the%20Hunting%20Symphony%2C%20a%20piece%20by%20Mozart's%20father%20Leopold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A225%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-europe-66705222%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Opposition%20Stands%20to%20Gain%20More%20From%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Move%20to%20Unify%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposing%20any%20decision%20that%20has%20been%20sprung%20on%20a%20country%20by%20its%20government%20without%20prior%20discussion%20is%20a%20reflex%20action%20among%20opposition%20parties%20in%20all%20democracies.%20So%20it%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%2C%20the%20only%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20whom%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20invited%20to%20join%20the%20eight%20member%20panel%20that%20it%20is%20setting%20up%2C%20ostensibly%20to%20study%20but%20in%20reality%20to%20whitewash%2C%20the%20re-unification%20of%20central%20and%20state%20elections%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDivorced%20from%20its%20present%20political%20context%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20not%20welcome%20the%20proposal%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections.%20The%20move%20will%20halve%20the%20presently%20crippling%20electioneering%20expenses%20for%20political%20parties.%20And%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20need%20to%20raise%20money%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20been%20coming%20from%20clandestine%20and%20criminal%20sources%20ever%20since%20the%20ban%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20put%20on%20company%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20in%201970.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReunification%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20also%20make%20it%20far%20easier%20for%20a%20future%20government%20to%20set%20up%20a%20state%20financed%20and%20publicly%20audited%20system%20of%20election%20financing.%20This%20would%20not%20only%20weaken%20and%2C%20over%20time%2C%20eliminate%20the%20nexus%20between%20crime%20and%20politics%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20also%20open%20the%20way%20for%20reforms%20in%20the%20police%20and%20lower%20administration%20that%20will%20cleanse%20the%20government%20of%20corruption%20and%20make%20it%20serve%20the%20people.%20It%20would%20also%20lengthen%20the%20time%20horizon%20over%20which%20government%20policies%20will%20need%20to%20bear%20fruit%3B%20restore%20the%20Centre-State%20co-ordination%20in%20policy%20making%20that%20was%20severely%20weakened%20by%20the%20separation%20of%20central%20from%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20facilitate%20structural%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felections-2024-india-most-dangerous-phase%5C%22%3EAs%20the%202024%20Elections%20Approach%2C%20India%20Is%20Entering%20the%20Most%20Dangerous%20Phase%20of%20Its%20Existence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20enacted%20with%20necessary%20safeguards%2C%20it%20will%20also%20put%20a%20brake%20on%20opportunistic%20defections%20from%20political%20parties.%20The%20most%20necessary%20of%20these%20safeguards%20will%20be%20an%20automatic%20declaration%20of%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20till%20the%20next%20general%20election%20in%20any%20state%20where%20the%20government%20has%20been%20brought%20down%20by%20defections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20reasons%20for%20taking%20this%20sudden%20decision%2C%20however%2C%20have%20little%20to%20do%20with%20better%20governance.%20He%20has%20taken%20it%20because%20he%20is%20aware%20that%20the%20BJP%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20suffering%20the%20same%20fate%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20possibly%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20that%20it%20suffered%20in%20Karnataka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20therefore%20understandably%20wary%20of%20going%20into%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20a%20string%20of%20electoral%20defeats%20in%20major%20states%20behind%20him.%20So%20he%20has%20decided%20to%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%20%E2%80%93%20avoid%20four%20important%20state%20elections%20that%20his%20party%20could%20lose%2C%20and%20hold%20a%20combined%20national%20and%20state%20election%20with%20the%20prestige%20of%20the%20G-20%20presidency%20and%20its%20grand%20conference%20in%20Delhi%20to%20buoy%20him%2C%20delivering%20both%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20to%20his%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%2C%20Fourth%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INDIA%20coalition%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20one-election%20proposal%20is%20therefore%20understandable.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20short-sighted%20because%20unifying%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20will%20resolve%20the%20most%20knotty%20problem%20that%20the%20alliance%20is%20facing%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20next%20general%20election%20and%20greatly%20improve%20its%20chances%20of%20victory.%20This%20problem%20is%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20to%20its%20constituent%20parties%20in%20each%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%20showed%2C%20the%20coalition%20is%20determined%20to%20field%20only%20one%20candidate%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20each%20constituency.%20But%20it%20has%20yet%20to%20decide%20from%20which%20party%2C%20and%20on%20what%20basis%20the%20candidate%20should%20be%20chosen.%20At%20the%20Patna%20meeting%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamta%20Bannerjee%20had%20told%20the%20press%20that%20the%20alliance%20would%20set%20up%20coordination%20committees%20that%20would%20first%20decide%20the%20principles%20they%20would%20follow%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20and%20then%20use%20these%20to%20choose%20the%20party%20and%20candidate%20for%20each%20constituency.%20Today%2C%20two%20more%20alliance%20meetings%20later%2C%20that%20process%20is%20only%20about%20to%20begin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20foot-dragging%20is%20taking%20place%20because%20the%20party%20leaders%20have%20not%20found%20a%20way%20to%20cross%20the%20main%20hurdle%20they%20face%3A%20how%20to%20retain%20the%20loyalty%20and%20support%20of%20their%20cadres%20in%20the%20constituencies%20that%20they%20have%20ceded%20to%20an%20ally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20problem%20would%20not%20have%20arisen%20if%20there%20had%20been%20a%20system%20of%20state%20financing%20of%20elections%20like%20the%20one%20Western%20Europe.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20parties%20have%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20local%20financiers%20whom%20they%20offer%20government%20contracts%20and%20other%20favours%20if%20their%20party%20comes%20to%20power.%20This%20clientelist%20system%20starts%20breaking%20down%20if%20the%20financiers%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20party%2C%20or%20in%20its%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20win.%20It%20ceases%20to%20exist%20when%20the%20party%20has%20no%20horse%20in%20the%20race.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20Modi%20has%20unwittingly%20offered%20INDIA%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20dilemma.%20This%20would%20confine%20the%20seat%20sharing%20between%20political%20parties%20only%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20allow%20full%20competition%20to%20continue%20between%20them%20sin%20the%20various%20state%20assemblies%20and%20also%20require%20them%20to%20make%20a%20clear%20demarcation%20between%20national%20and%20local%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParty%20cadres%20can%20then%20be%20instructed%20to%20emphasise%20national%20issues%20in%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20where%20their%20party%20is%20fielding%20candidates%20for%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%2C%20and%20to%20place%20greater%20stress%20on%20state%20and%20local%20issues%20in%20those%20where%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20been%20allotted%20to%20another%20member%20of%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-stands-to-gain-more-from-modis-move-to-unify-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%2C%20Modi%20has%20unwittingly%20offered%20INDIA%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20dilemma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-stands-to-gain-more-from-modis-move-to-unify-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Political%20Ethics%20of%20the%20Indian%20Political%20Right%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F09155320%2FIMG_0444.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20challenge%20in%20recognising%2C%20realising%2C%20and%20endorsing%20place%20of%20emotions%20is%20how%20they%20do%20not%20become%20templates%20for%20righteous%20lawlessness%20and%20majoritarianism%E2%80%A6Emotive%20majority%20today%20is%20an%20undeniable%20reality%20in%20most%20of%20the%20world%2C%20but%20the%20consequences%20and%20the%20way%20they%20can%20be%20nudged%20towards%20compassionate%20cohabitation%20is%20still%20an%20open%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20these%20words%2C%20political%20theorist%20Ajay%20Gudavarthy%2C%20in%20his%20recent%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitics%2C%20Ethics%20and%20Emotions%20in%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20attempts%20to%20unpack%20the%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20emotive%20questions%20that%20may%20help%20one%20understand%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20political%20right%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20questions%20may%20also%20interest%20us%20in%20the%20current%20global%20context%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20rightwing%20conservatism%2C%20while%20studying%20how%20people%20cutting%20across%20castes%20and%20classes%20perceive%20the%20rightwing%20construct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20364px)%2085vw%2C%20364px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02170949%2F61Ux26RKqHL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22364%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02170949%2F61Ux26RKqHL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20654w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02170949%2F61Ux26RKqHL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg%20196w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22557%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolitics%2C%20Ethics%20and%20Emotions%20in%20%E2%80%98New%20India%2C%E2%80%99%20Ajay%20Gudavarthy%2C%20Routledge%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20a%20bio-political%20normative%20lens%2C%20the%20author%20puts%20forward%20a%20critical%20question%20in%20the%20book%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20we%20remobilise%20and%20occupy%20ethics%20and%20emotions%20that%20are%20not%20majoritarian%2C%20ethics%20that%20do%20not%20eschew%20responsibility%2C%20and%20emotions%20that%20do%20not%20produce%20a%20valorised%20self%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Gudavarthy%2C%20this%20may%20be%20particularly%20relevant%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20contemporary%20political%20space%20and%20the%20everyday%20ethics%20of%20being%20in%20India%2C%20when%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20under%20Narendra%20Modi-Amit%20Shah%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cjustifiably%20mobilising%20emotions%20and%20striking%20a%20chord%20with%20a%20majority%2C%20but%20that%20is%20necessarily%20illiberal%20in%20nature%20and%20producing%20ethics%20that%20are%20blatantly%20majoritarian%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%E2%80%99s%20thesis%20is%20densely%20layered%20in%20three%20distinct%20parts%20(Part%20I%3A%20Politics%20and%20Emotions%2C%20Part%20II%3A%20Economy%20and%20Ethics%2C%20and%20Part%20III%3A%20Ethical%20Emotions%3F)%20and%20has%20been%20written%20in%20contribution%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Reshaping%20India%E2%80%99%20book%20series%20produced%20by%20the%20Samruddha%20Bharat%20Foundation%20with%20Routledge%2C%20Taylor%20and%20Francis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20those%20reading%20Gudavarthy%E2%80%99s%20work%20for%20the%20first%20time%20may%20find%20more%20contextual%20meaning%20to%20this%20text%20after%20perceiving%20this%20as%20a%20sequel%20to%20his%20previous%20offering%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20After%20Modi%3A%20Populism%20and%20the%20Right%20(2018).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20missing%20woods%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20its%20initial%20background%20and%20interest%20is%20situated%20in%20studying%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20political%20%3Cem%3Er%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Eight%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ei.e.%20the%20BJP%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egovernmentality%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20in%20explaining%20their%20regime%E2%80%99s%20complex%20experiments%20with%20the%20everyday%20political%20ethics%20of%20being%20built%20around%20the%20tradecraft%20of%20seducing%20the%20emotive%20majority.%20This%20can%20perhaps%20help%20one%20explain%20a%20persistent%20rise%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20own%20popularity%2C%20accentuated%20by%20the%20emotive%20politics%20of%20thoughtless%20belief.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20interesting%20aspect%20of%20viewing%20the%20%E2%80%98emotive%E2%80%99%20influence%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20amongst%20the%20larger%20Indian%20electorate%20(especially%20the%20Hindi%20belt)%20despite%20the%20nature%20of%20social%20or%20economic%20issues%20that%20afflict%20the%20same%20majority%2C%20according%20to%20Gudavarthy%2C%20is%20established%20by%20understanding%20what%20the%20right%20invests%20is%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emorality%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20what%20a%20majority%20works%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20everyday%20ethics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20quote%20from%20Brent%20Adkins%20(below)%20is%20particularly%20striking%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20morality%20functions%20according%20to%20principle%20while%20an%20ethics%20functions%20according%20to%20experimentation.%20A%20morality%20presupposes%20a%20discontinuity%20between%20principle%20and%20action%2C%20while%20an%20ethics%20presupposes%20a%20continuity%20of%20action%20and%20character.%20A%20morality%20tells%20one%20what%20one%20ought%20to%20do%2C%20while%20an%20ethics%20asks%20what%20one%20might%20do%E2%80%9D%20(Brent%20Adkins%2C%202015%3B%20p147)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20somewhere%2C%20in%20the%20complex%20oscillations%20of%20a%20layered%20thesis%20that%20attempts%20to%20deal%20in%20ethics%2C%20morality%2C%20and%20emotions%2C%20all%20at%20once%2C%20there%20are%20voids%20and%20silences%20that%20emerge%20in%20Gudavarthy%E2%80%99s%20thesis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20everyday%20ethics%20of%20being%20and%20what%20may%20help%20explain%20the%20average%20Hindu%20voter%E2%80%99s%20(as%20part%20of%20the%20seduced%20emotive%20majority)%20motivational%20rationality%20can%20be%20studied%20by%20viewing%20the%20application%20of%20Dharma%2C%20Dharam%2C%20Kama%2C%20Karma.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brahmanical%20cloak%20designed%20to%20guide%20each%20of%20these%20has%20been%20deeply%20politicised%20by%20the%20Modi-Shah-RSS%20regime%20which%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20establish%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20considers%20a%20persistent%20effort%20to%20influence%20these%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98emotive%20(Hindu)%20majority%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20thus%20allows%20one%20to%20%E2%80%98clean%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98teach%20minorities%20a%20lesson%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20establish%20a%20masculine%20muscularity%20in%20a%20hyper-nationalist%20wave.%20It%20is%20all%20part%20of%20a%20political%20project%20that%20builds%20itself%20on%20a%20new%20morality%2C%20the%20ethics%20of%20being%20for%20emotions%20(rage%2C%20anger%2C%20violence)%20to%20be%20experienced%20and%20realised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20normative%20axis%20misses%20in%20presenting%20a%20robust%20critique%20of%20liberal%20foundations%20and%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20that%20maybe%20less%20relevant%20for%20the%20Indian%20polity%20or%20society%20%E2%80%93%20is%20there%20is%20more%20left%20to%20be%20said%20on%20what%20drives%20a%20foundational%20link%20between%20the%20interplay%20of%20Morality-Ethics-Emotions%20(MEE)%20with%20the%20governing%20dynamics%20of%20Dharam%2C%20Dharma%2C%20Kama%20and%20Karma.%20The%20latter%20defines%20India%E2%80%99s%20socio-political%20landscape%20underplayed%20by%20a%20theory%20of%20power%2C%20faith%2C%20cultural%20propriety%2C%20memory%20and%20language.%20All%20of%20these%2C%20in%20some%20way%20or%20another%2C%20shape%20the%20everyday%20political%20ethics%20of%20being%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emajority%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20non-emotive%20here%20also%20entwine%20with%20the%20emotive%20class%2C%20while%20working%20as%20templates%20of%20self-representation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20empirical%20void%20that%20extrapolates%20from%20the%20normative%20void%20is%20the%20weak%20link%20drawn%20between%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20political%20r%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eight%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20narrativising%20an%20alternative%20%E2%80%98truth%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20satiated%20need%20of%20the%20emotive%20majority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20a%20majority%20will%20forget%20the%20acquired%20knowledge%20of%20the%20past%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98new%E2%80%99%20truth%20to%20be%20discovered.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20right%20has%20a%20complex%20techno-political%20relationship%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20the%20contemporary%20tools%20and%20mechanisms%20of%20the%20current%20information%20order%20and%20digital%20technological%20infrastructure.%20It%20is%20the%20same%20structure%20that%20the%20right%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eweaponises%20on%20day-to-day%20basis.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENormative%20vision%20and%20ideas%20of%20ethics%20or%20morality%20are%20mediated%20through%20symbolism%20that%20can%20be%20manipulated%20through%20media%20and%20information%20flow.%20This%20has%20been%20most%20vital%20for%20the%20Modi-Shah%20double%20engine%20to%20not%20just%20acquire%20power%2C%20but%20also%20consolidate%20it%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBuilding%20the%20thesis%20forward%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStrongmen%20Saviours%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20Abhinav%20Padmanabhan%2C%20our%20own%20comparative%20analysis%20of%20the%20recent%20wave%20of%20rightwing%20populist%20movements%20across%20the%20world%20was%20explained%20through%20a%20distinct%20pattern%20exhibiting%20features%20that%20have%20been%20unique%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20right-wing%20movements%20(as%20against%20left-wing%20movements%20of%20the%20past).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20purpose%20then%20was%20to%20provide%20a%20comparative%20socio-political%2C%20economic%20explanation%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20populist%20beliefs%20and%20anti-political%20elite%20sentiment%20that%20has%20not%20captured%20much%20of%20the%20Western%20and%20non-Western%20sphere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pyramid%20constructed%20below%2C%20drawn-built%20on%20our%20book%E2%80%99s%20research%20may%20offer%20some%20insights%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02213823%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-9.38.04-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02213823%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-9.38.04-PM.png%20956w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02213823%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-9.38.04-PM-300x190.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671216%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22425%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conceptual%20pyramid%20attempts%20to%20unpack%20features%20of%20right-wing%20populism%2C%20operating%20under%20the%20guise-envelope%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98ideological%20populism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(ideologically%20aligned%20populist%20movements)%2C%20which%20has%20a%20distinct%20meaning%20(see%20a%20more%20detailed%20explainer%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Flive%2FPgPnQ3RmdqA%3Ffeature%3Dshare%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eideological%20populism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0refers%20to%20the%20unchecked-unabated%20rise%20of%20an%20ideology%2C%20the%20marginalization%20of%20its%20moderate%20factions%2C%20involving%20the%20development%20of%20a%20cult-personality%20that%20infuses%20shades%20of%20populism%20into%20it.%20Normatively%2C%20this%20can%20be%20ideologically%20aligned%20towards%20the%20%E2%80%98political%20left%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98political%20right%E2%80%99.%20The%20distinct%20characteristics%20of%20rightwing%20populism%20at%20least%20the%20way%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewe%20have%20observed%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20India%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20Brazil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edid%20see%20certain%20common%20features%2C%20across%20different%20times%20and%20spaces.%20I%20explained%20a%20few%20of%20these%20factors%2Ffeatures%20from%20the%20pyramid%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fright-wing-populism-towards-a-new-theory-of-economic-change%23read-more%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20factors%20contribute%20to%20the%20right%E2%80%99s%20authoritative%20rise%20to%20majoritarian%20power.%20They%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFailure%20of%20Neoliberalism%20(supply-side%20economics%20of%20the%2090s)%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20origins%20of%20each%20of%20these%20movements%20are%20in%20the%20economic%20discontents%20of%20neoliberalism%20or%20the%20nature%20of%20supply-side%20economics%20(externally%20influenced%20by%20the%20West%2FWashington%20Consensus%20style%20reform%20packages)%20pursued%20in%20the%201990s.%20Studies%20from%20scholars%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESides%20et%20al.%20(2018)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENorris%20%26amp%3B%20Inglehart%20(2019)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMargalit%20(2019)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0also%20explain%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20wave%20of%20rise%20in%20religious%20conservatism%20or%20religious%20orthodoxy%20(from%20Hindutva%20to%20Orthodox%20Islam%20to%20Evangelical%20Catholicism)%20that%20aided%20the%20rise%20of%20each%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20either%20belonged%20to%20political%20parties%20or%20to%20orthodox-religious%20based%20organisations%20which%20ensured%20an%20undercurrent%20of%20religious%20conservatism.%20This%20made%20more%20people%20open%20to%20acknowledging%2C%20practicing%20or%20promoting%20%E2%80%98extreme%E2%80%99%20beliefs.%20I%20explain%20more%20about%20this%20phenomenon%20(as%20seen%20in%20India%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20Brazil)%20in%20a%20lecture%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Flive%2FPgPnQ3RmdqA%3Ffeature%3Dshare%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egiven%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trigger%20factor%20which%20led%20to%20the%20mass-protest%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20each%20strongman%20figure%20from%20Modi%20to%20Bolsonaro%2C%20was%20often%20related%20to%20either%20a%20series%20of%20big%20public%20corruption%20episodes%20or%20reported%20scandal(s)%20in%20the%20home%20country%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20political%20environment%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20opportunity%20for%20mass%20support%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20alternative%20imagination%20of%20power.%20A%20leader%2C%20someone%20outside%20the%20status%20quo%20ruling%20political%20elite%2C%20came%20to%20power%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20mass%20popularity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20India%20to%20Brazil%2C%20each%20of%20the%20countries%20we%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ediscuss%20in%20the%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saw%20episodes%20of%20public%20corruption%20via%20scandals%20or%20were%20operating%20in%20a%20widely%20perceived%20environment%20of%20corruption%20that%20spurred%20the%20choice%20of%20voting%20for%20an%20alternative.%20This%20was%20also%20seen%20with%20the%20protest%20vote%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%202016%20US%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20weaponisation%20of%20social%20media%20in%20a%20new%20tech-enabled%20information%20order%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20rightwing%20populists%20to%20continue%20feeding%20an%20alternative%2C%20post-truth%20rhetorical%20narrative%20of%20%E2%80%98us%20versus%20them%E2%80%99%2C%20pivoted%20on%20the%20axis%20of%20immigration.%20Surveillance%20capitalism%20made%20this%20possible%20too%20under%20a%20new%20nexus%20of%20private%20capital-state%20relationship%20which%20supported%20strongmen%20figures%20in%20power%20through%20social%20media%20and%20digitised%20surveillance%20tools.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFocus%20on%20privatisation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nature%20of%20fiscal%20policy%20brought%20by%20each%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eright-wing%20populist%20strongman%20figures%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20drastically%20varied%20when%20compared%20to%20earlier%20regimes%20of%20populist%20movements%20(as%20seen%20in%20Latin%20America).%20Earlier%20strongman%20leaderships%20were%20influenced%20by%20a%20theory%20of%20economic%20and%20political%20change%20belonging%20to%20pro-welfare%2C%20left-leaning%20policies%2C%20which%20in%20some%20instances%20like%20Venezuela%20made%20governments%20fiscally%20indebted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latest%20variant%20of%20rightwing%20populism%20has%20seen%20a%20promotion%20of%20privatisation%20and%20reorientation%20of%20previous%20state-private%20capital%20elite%20relationships.%20This%20has%20been%20pursued%20with%20gradual%20disinvestment%20of%20public%20assets%20and%20government%20ownership%20of%20resources%2C%20including%20a%20de-funding%20of%20social%20programmes%20targeted%20for%20job%20creation%2C%20human%20capital%20development-healthcare%20and%20education.%20This%20is%20widely%20seen%20in%20the%20fiscal%20choices%20made%20by%20most%20strongman%20figures%20like%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20strongmen%20continue%20to%20strike%20a%20chord%20with%20extremely%20low-income%20voters%20in%20some%20of%20the%20lesser%20developed%20states%20and%20provinces%20thanks%20to%20the%20political%20use%20of%20targeted%20beneficiary-based%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20however%20be%20observed%20that%20none%20of%20this%20so-called%20welfare%20spending%20is%20aimed%20at%20the%20upward%20mobility%20of%20the%20low-income%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOn%20contestations%20within%3A%20Hyper-globalism%20and%20ideological%20populism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDani%20Rodrik%E2%80%99s%20recent%20work%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrodrik.scholar.harvard.edu%2Fsites%2Fscholar.harvard.edu%2Ffiles%2Fdani-rodrik%2Ffiles%2Fon_productivism.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20offers%20useful%20insights%20on%20at%20least%20addressing%20one%20of%20these%20%E2%80%98contested%E2%80%99%20conceptual%20questions%3A%20Why%20did%20globalisation%20of%20the%20post-1990s%20variant%20fuel%20a%20certain%20wave%20of%20populism%2C%20one%20that%20spread%20far%20across%20the%20west%20and%20the%20east%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Rodrik%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20what%20are%20the%20mechanisms%20through%20which%20globalisation%20fuels%20populism.%20Answering%20this%20question%20requires%20a%20fully%20fleshed-out%20model%20of%20political%20economy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20globalisation%20is%20not%20just%20one%20thing.%20We%20can%20distinguish%20between%20international%20trade%2C%20international%20finance%2C%20and%20international%20labour%20flows%2C%20specifically.%20How%20does%20each%20one%20of%20these%20facets%20of%20globalisation%20work%20its%20way%20through%20the%20political%20system%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThird%2C%20globalisation%20is%20clearly%20not%20the%20only%20economic%20shock%20that%20creates%20redistributive%20effects%20or%20economic%20anxiety%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20may%20not%20even%20be%20the%20most%20important%20one.%20Why%20does%20globalisation%20appear%20to%20have%20an%20outsized%20effect%20on%20politics%20compared%20to%2C%20say%2C%20technological%20change%20or%20regular%20business%20cycles%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20aspects%20are%20studied%20more%20empirically%20by%20Rodrik%20in%20the%20framework%20created%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04155427%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.51.45.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22694%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04155427%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.51.45.png%20912w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04155427%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.51.45-300x256.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22592%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20according%20to%20Rodrik%E2%80%99s%20analytical%20framework%20above%2C%20and%20most%20directly%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeconomic%20dislocation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0can%20determine%20voters%E2%80%99%20preferences%20for%20policies%20and%20leaders%20(arrow%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20Voters%20in%20a%20region%20where%20employment%20prospects%20have%20been%20adversely%20affected%20by%20a%20rise%20in%20imports%20may%20choose%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20for%20a%20politician%20who%20advocates%20protectionism%20and%20a%20tougher%20line%20against%20foreign%20exporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20economic%20dislocation%20may%20shape%20voters%E2%80%99%20preferences%20indirectly%20through%20the%20effect%20it%20has%20on%20identity%20or%20the%20salience%20of%20certain%20cultural%20values%20(arrow%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eb%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20Concretely%2C%20economic%20shocks%20can%20heighten%20feelings%20of%20insecurity%2C%20inducing%20voters%20to%20make%20sharper%20distinctions%20between%20insiders%20(%E2%80%9Cus%E2%80%9D)%20and%20ethnic%2C%20religious%2C%20or%20racial%20outsiders%20(%E2%80%9Cthem%E2%80%9D).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20lead%20voters%20to%20yearn%20for%20an%20earlier%20era%20of%20prosperity%20and%20stability%2C%20increasing%20the%20political%20salience%20of%20traditional%20cultural%20values%20and%20hierarchies.%20And%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20generate%20wider%20economic%20and%20social%20gaps%20within%20a%20nation%2C%20economic%20shocks%20may%20reinforce%20more%20local%2C%20less%20encompassing%20identities.%20To%20the%20extent%20that%20such%20effects%20operate%2C%20political%20preferences%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20cultural%20values%20do%20in%20fact%20have%20deeper%20economic%20roots.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplored%20some%20of%20these%20links%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20the%20discontents%20of%20neoliberal%20economics%20and%20populism%20in%20the%20context%20of%20India%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20Russia%2C%20however%2C%20there%20were%20other%20factors%20complementing%20this%20and%20Rodrik%E2%80%99s%20framework%20shared%20above.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20additional%20causal%20factors%20are%20instances%20of%20large-scale%20public%20corruption%20(or%20an%20environment%20of%20an%20ostensibly%20corrupt%20political%20elite)%2C%20and%20a%20rise%20in%20religious%20conservatism%20contributed%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20rightwing%20populist%20movements%20that%20subsequently%20brought%20leaders%20like%20Modi%2C%20Bolsonaro%2C%20and%20Putin%2C%20to%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20critical%20need%20to%20put%20these%20explanations%20in%20perspective%20and%20context%20while%20building%20upon%20what%20Gudavarthy%E2%80%99s%20frame%20of%20reasoning%20brings%20in%20light.%20This%20must%20be%20done%20by%20adopting%20a%20more%20neo-subaltern%20approach%20that%20is%20grounded%20in%20interpreting%20a%20random%20person%E2%80%99s%20preference%20for%20the%20political%20right.%20One%20must%20also%20see%20how%20the%20right%20operates%20in%20influencing%20one%E2%80%99s%20everyday%20ethics%20distinctively%20and%20assertively%2C%20while%20thriving%20on%20the%20anxieties%2C%20fears%2C%20and%20insecurities%20of%20the%20emotive%20majority.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20in%20also%20understanding%20how%20the%20moral-ethical%20core%20of%20an%20average%20Hindu%20voter%20subscribing%20to%20the%20populist%20belief%20remains%20influenced%20by%20the%20applied%20role%20of%20Dharam%2C%20Dharma%2C%20Kama%20and%20Karma%20in%20everyday%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20and%20director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F09155320%2FIMG_0444.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fthe-political-ethics-of-the-indian-political-right%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ajay%20Gudavarthy%E2%80%99s%20recent%20book%2C%20'Politics%2C%20Ethics%20and%20Emotions%20in%20'New%20India''%20attempts%20to%20unpack%20the%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20emotive%20questions%20in%20understanding%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rise%20to%20power%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1