Consequently%2C%20discovering%20the%20ideal%20location%20to%20establish%20this%20haven%20can%20be%20an%20enormous%20undertaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20quest%20for%20the%20right%20size%20and%20location%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20distinct%20sense%20of%20eager%20anticipation%20and%20a%20few%20heart-fluttering%20instances%20when%20you%20step%20into%20a%20residence%20and%20realize%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20might%20be%20the%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20precise%20moment%20occurred%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20Anuradha%20and%20Kartik%20Budhraja%20when%20they%20laid%20eyes%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20situated%20in%20the%20Saroga%20village%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F116393%2Fhimachal-pradesh-electric-buses-hrtc-road-transport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20overjoyed%20upon%20our%20initial%20glimpse%20of%20the%20land.%20It%20appeared%20as%20though%20it%20had%20been%20plucked%20from%20a%20fairy%20tale.%20We%20exchanged%20glances%2C%20and%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20we%20both%20understood%20that%20this%20would%20be%20the%20place%20where%20we%20would%20nurture%20our%20daughters%2C%E2%80%9D%20reminisces%20Anuradha%20Budhraja%2C%20when%20speaking%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELong-standing%20dream%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Himalayas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%20living%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20overlooking%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311053%2Fdushyant-vashisht-turned-cottage-to-sustainable-homestay-bir-terraces-uttarakhand-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimalayan%20ranges%20with%20nature%20around%20us%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20our%20dream.%20This%20dream%20became%20more%20urgent%20when%20we%20visited%20Thanedar%20in%